/// success : 1
/// data : [{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/What-Every-Home-Buyer-Needs-to-Know-About-GujRERA"},"id":289,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"What-Every-Home-Buyer-Needs-to-Know-About-GujRERA","image":"banner_1705120936_54.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1705120936_54.jpg","banner_title":"Homebuyers' Guide to RERA","title":"Homebuyers' Guide to RERA","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Making informed decisions and ensuring transparency are important when buying a home. The Real Estate Regulatory Authority empowers homebuyers during the home-buying process.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>What is the Real Estate Regulatory Authority (RERA)?</strong><br />\nThe Real Estate Regulatory Authority (RERA) is a government body that regulates the real estate industry in India. They provide homebuyers with the assurance that the property they are buying is genuine and that the seller is adhering to the rules and regulations.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>They also provide homebuyers with information about the seller, the property, and the purchase process.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Find out how you can check homes on RERA to make an informed decision that aligns with what you are looking for.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This act passed by parliament in India and was given assent by the President on 25th March 2016.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In order to facilitate and oversee real estate in Gujarat, the Gujarat government has established the Gujarat Real Estate Company known as Gujerera.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>How to check details on RERA?</strong><br />\nTo get started, visit the official RERA website.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Visit - https://gujrera.gujarat.gov.in/</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>You can search for an agent or builder by typing their name in the search box at the top-center part. Here, you can enter the name or registration number of the project you want to learn more about.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Click on the relevant project and verify the details.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>RERA provides a comprehensive overview, including project status, approvals, carpet area, possession date, etc.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>You can also check the track record of the builder, their past projects, and any legal issues.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Ensure that you go through these documents, including the title deed, layout plans, and construction quality specifications.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Visit the complaints section on the RERA website to find information about any disputes or litigations related to the project.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Final Thought</strong><br />\nAs a home buyer, you can make informed decisions by leveraging RERA to check homes. Using it, you get a transparent picture of the real estate landscape, which helps you to choose the ideal property with transparency.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For those seeking not just a home but a lifestyle crafted with precision, the Shivalik Group holds a prominent position in Ahmedabad&#39;s real estate sector.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With a legacy of excellence, Shivalik Group invites you to explore their projects built with quality and commitment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Make your home-buying journey memorable, informed, and rewarding with Shivalik Group&mdash;the hallmark of trust in Ahmedabad&#39;s real estate sector.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">-&nbsp;Kishan Thakkar</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"What Every Home Buyer Needs to Know About GujRERA?","seo_description":": Get a comprehensive guide on how to check homes on RERA as a home buyer. Learn how to confirm the authenticity of properties and make sure you get the best deal.","seo_keywords":"Home, Office, RERA, RERA Area, Real Estate, Shivalik, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1705121029_95.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1705121029_95.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Home","tag_lower":"home"},{"text":"Office","tag_lower":"office"},{"text":"Area","tag_lower":"area"},{"text":"RERA","tag_lower":"rera"},{"text":"RERA Area","tag_lower":"rera area"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Home","Office","Area","RERA","RERA Area","Real Estate","Shivalik","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Home,Office,Area,RERA,RERA Area,Real Estate,Shivalik,Ahmedabad","published_time":1705084200,"published_date":"13 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1705120936,"date_format":"","date_time":"10:12 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"13 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"10:12 AM"},"updated_at":"Jan 13, 2024","updated_at_time":1705121058,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1705298779","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/COMMON-AREA--COMMON-OWNERSHIP-COMMON-QUESTIONS"},"id":284,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"12","slug":"COMMON-AREA--COMMON-OWNERSHIP-COMMON-QUESTIONS","image":"banner_1704799121_7.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1704799121_7.jpg","banner_title":"Common Area - Common Ownership – Common Questions","title":"Common Area - Common Ownership – Common Questions","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Author - <strong>Adv. Lokesh Shah</strong></p>\n\n<p>Mobile Number -&nbsp;8000647068</p>\n\n<p>Email id -&nbsp;lokesh@gujreraexperts.com</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In the realm of real estate, numerous terms are associated with residential complexes. One such term that frequently approaches is &#39;common area.&#39; Simply put, a common area refers to a shared space within a residential or commercial complex that is collectively funded by all its residents. In this context, every &nbsp;owner in the Project is considered a co-owner of these communal spaces, and the ownership is distributed equally among all the residents.</p>\n\n<p>If a Developer /Promoter offers you the super-built area of a house, the entire area, including the common areas, is included in it. <strong>As per section &nbsp;2(n) of the &nbsp;RERA Act, 2016, &ldquo;Common Area&rdquo; includes:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The entire land for the real estate project, or if the project is developed in phases and registration under the RERA is sought for a phase, the entire land for that particular phase.</li>\n\t<li>Staircases, lift, elevators, elevator lobbies, fire escapes, and common entrances and exits of buildings.</li>\n\t<li>Common terraces and basements, parks, play areas, open parking areas, and common storage spaces.</li>\n\t<li>The premises for lodging of persons who are employed for the management of the property, including accommodation for watchmen and ward staff, or for the lodging of community service personnel.</li>\n\t<li>All community and commercial facilities as provided in the real estate project.</li>\n\t<li>Installations of central services such as electricity, gas, water and sanitation, air-conditioning and incineration, and systems for water conservation and renewable energy.</li>\n\t<li>Water tanks, pumps, motors, compressors, fans, ducts, and all apparatus connected with installations for common use.</li>\n\t<li>Other portions of the project necessary or convenient for its maintenance, safety, etc. and in common use.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>1. Not only RERA but Apartment Act also have some guidelines for common area:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Before the association of allotters takes over, the developer is responsible for preserving common areas.</li>\n\t<li>The responsibility for the common area maintenance falls to all members of society.</li>\n\t<li>The landlord is liable for the maintenance of the common areas in the case of commercial property.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>When it comes to an area that is shared by all there are various questions attached to it. We offers you answer to all your queries as follow:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>2. Who&rsquo;s Responsible for the Maintenance of the Common Area?</strong></p>\n\n<p>All allottees are equally accountable for open areas and their maintenance. The Real Estate Act (RERA) specifies that it should be the responsibility of every allottee to make payments to maintain the property and the premises. All citizens collect a stipulated fee and this goes towards operational expenses undertaken to protect the community areas.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>3.&nbsp;Can It Be Possible to Inherit and Pass Common Area?</strong></p>\n\n<p>No, It is not possible to inherit or transfer common areas and facilities by sale, mortgage, lease, gift, or swap, along with an undivided interest in common areas to any third party. The reference may be made to the decision of this Court in case of <a href=\"https://www.casemine.com/judgement/in/56e66a98607dba6b53436781\">Harikrushnadas Chhaganlal, Nanalal &amp; Ishwardas Mohanlal Seva Samaj Trust v. Vinodchandra G. Vaghela</a> reported in <strong>2010 (2) GLR 1820</strong> wherein at paras 4, 5 and 6 it was observed as under:</p>\n\n<p><strong>&ldquo;4.</strong> It is an admitted fact that the society has sold the land of the common plot to the petitioner. It can hardly be disputed that the land of the common plot in any residential society is meant for common use and common purposes of all members of the society, and all members of the society, so far as common plot and common facilities and common area are concerned, they are holding joint and common interest in such portion. It is not the case of the respondent society that the land has been permitted to be used for creating of any common facilities for the members of the society.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>4. If you are not using common areas and services, do you pay maintenance charges?</strong></p>\n\n<p>According to the Apartment act, &lsquo;No apartment owners may exempt themselves from liability for their contribution towards the common expenses by waiver of the use or enjoyment of any of the common areas and facilities or by the abandonment of their apartment&rsquo; In simple words, &lsquo;yes&rsquo; it is mandatory for all to pay maintenance charges.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>5.&nbsp;Common Area to be utilized by all members.</strong></p>\n\n<p>In the Gujarat RERA &nbsp;judgement for the case law of Members of <strong>Nilkanth Villa Vs. Pari Infra</strong>, it was enacted that :</p>\n\n<p>A Common area between two concerned Projects was separated by a compound wall, and thus the common area was divided , and was the cause of complaint between the members of both the Projects, &nbsp;but later on through the Order of the Hon&rsquo;ble Authority , the common compound wall was ordered to be demolished and the common area was allowed to be used by both the Project members.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>6. How Can Common Areas Be Identified?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Information on the property on which the building was constructed and the common areas and amenities must be included in the sale documents of the apartment and its registration papers. It should also note whether the property is freehold property or leasehold and whether the lease period is a leasehold property. It should also include the percentage of an undivided interest in the common areas and services relating to the apartment. It must also explain the restricted common areas and services.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>7. Can Members Parking can be sold ?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Open Parking cannot be sold to the any particular allottee, as the open &nbsp;parking is considered as the common area as per the definition of &ldquo;<strong>Common area</strong>&rdquo;as per RERA Act. But covered parking is not considered as a part of the common area and thus it &nbsp;can be sold..</p>\n\n<p>Maharashtra &nbsp;Real Estate Regulatory Authority in the Complaint No. <strong>CC006000000089761</strong> &ndash; &nbsp;in the matter of Mr. Deepesh S Singh &nbsp;Vs M/s. Neelkanth Constructions &nbsp;, Ordered that &ldquo;With regard to the car parking, the MahaRERA directs that the respondent is entitled to sell only covered car parking and no cash money be demanded from the allottees.&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>8. Is It Possible to Sell Common Roof Rights Through a Developer?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Giving or selling exclusive rights to the terrace or rooftop is an unethical activity in a housing society. All other common terraces belong to a resident unless the terrace is attached to a unit. A terrace, if inaccessible from common areas, is private. It is not possible to buy or sell common terrace space and is, thus, not included in the floor area ratio (FAR).</p>\n\n<p>We trust that this article has addressed your inquiries regarding the common area. Should you require additional information about real estate, feel free to visit us for further assistance.</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags_array":"","tags_commaseparted":"","published_time":1704758400,"published_date":"09 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1704799122,"date_format":"","date_time":"04:48 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"09 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"04:48 PM"},"updated_at":"Jan 15, 2024","updated_at_time":1705298830,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1705298848","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Fractional-Ownership-in-Real-Estate-Unlocking-New-Horizons"},"id":283,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"12","slug":"Fractional-Ownership-in-Real-Estate-Unlocking-New-Horizons","image":"banner_1704787704_81.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1704787704_81.jpg","banner_title":"Fractional Ownership in Real Estate: Unlocking New Horizons","title":"Fractional Ownership in Real Estate: Unlocking New Horizons","description":"<p><input alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.reecosys.com/api/uploads/blog/2024/01/1704786480_CA_Harsh_Mehta.png\" style=\"width: 213px; height: 186px;\" type=\"image\" /></p>\n\n<p>Author - <strong>CA Harsh Mehta</strong></p>\n\n<p>Mobile Number :&nbsp;9998059270</p>\n\n<p>Email Id :&nbsp;harsh@gujreraexperts.com</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Fractional Ownership in Real Estate: Unlocking New Horizons</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Introduction</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>In recent years, fractional ownership has emerged as a revolutionary trend in real estate, transforming how individuals invest in and experience property ownership. This innovative approach offers flexibility and accessibility, reshaping traditional models.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Understanding Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>What is Fractional Ownership?</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Fractional ownership involves multiple investors jointly owning a high-value asset, like a property. Investors own shares representing a fraction of the asset, enabling investment in premium real estate without a substantial capital outlay.</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Mechanism Behind Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Properties are divided into shares through specialized platforms. Investors purchase these shares, gaining a portion of the property&#39;s value. This democratizes real estate investment, allowing broader participation.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Advantages of Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Diversification of Investment Portfolio</strong></p>\n\n<p>Fractional ownership enables diversification across multiple properties, reducing risk for investors.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Access to Premium Properties</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investors gain access to luxury real estate without the financial burden of sole ownership.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Hassle-Free Management</strong></p>\n\n<p>Professional management companies handle property maintenance, providing a hassle-free ownership experience.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Overcoming Challenges in Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Regulatory Considerations</strong></p>\n\n<p>Navigating legal frameworks is crucial. Seeking legal counsel and using reputable platforms help ensure compliance and mitigate risks.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Communication and Decision-Making</strong></p>\n\n<p>Effective communication and clear decision-making protocols are essential for successful fractional ownership.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>The Future of Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>As the real estate landscape evolves, fractional ownership is set to become integral to global investment strategies. The democratization of premium property access, coupled with technological advancements, positions it as transformative.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Types of Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Equity-Based Fractional Ownership</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investors hold actual equity in the property, establishing a direct link between property value and returns.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Time-Based Fractional Ownership</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investors purchase the right to use the property for specific periods, common for vacation properties.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tokenization in Fractional Ownership</strong></p>\n\n<p>Blockchain technology facilitates fractional ownership through digital tokens, streamlining transactions.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Crowdfunding Real Estate Ownership</strong></p>\n\n<p>Collective efforts of multiple investors fund property purchases, making real estate investment accessible.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Destination Clubs</strong></p>\n\n<p>Membership-based clubs offer access to a portfolio of luxury properties, combining equity and time-based ownership.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs)</strong></p>\n\n<p>Publicly traded entities allowing indirect ownership of diverse real estate portfolios.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>The Rise of Fractional Ownership Platforms</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Fractional ownership platforms have transformed the real estate industry by breaking down traditional barriers.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Accessibility and Inclusivity</strong></p>\n\n<p>Platforms make real estate investment accessible to a broader audience, expanding opportunities.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Technology Integration</strong></p>\n\n<p>Blockchain and online platforms bring transparency and security to transactions.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Diverse Investment Options</strong></p>\n\n<p>Platforms offer a range of investment options, catering to different preferences.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Liquidity and Exit Strategies</strong></p>\n\n<p>Fractional ownership provides enhanced liquidity, allowing investors to adjust positions more readily.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Risk Mitigation</strong></p>\n\n<p>Platforms implement risk mitigation strategies, ensuring a more secure investment environment.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Community Engagement</strong></p>\n\n<p>Platforms foster a sense of community, allowing investors to connect, share experiences, and gain insights.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Regulatory Compliance</strong></p>\n\n<p>Reputable platforms prioritize compliance with regulations, ensuring a structured and secure environment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>The Impact of Fractional Ownership on the Real Estate Market</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Fractional ownership has introduced a paradigm shift, democratizing real estate investment and increasing liquidity.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Democratization of Real Estate Investment</strong><br />\nFractional ownership broadens the investor base, injecting diversity into the real estate market.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Increased Liquidity and Flexibility</strong><br />\nPlatforms introduce liquidity, enabling easier buying and selling of property shares.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Rise of Micro-Investing</strong><br />\nMicro-investing allows investors to allocate smaller amounts across multiple properties, promoting inclusivity.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Transformed Use of Premium Properties</strong><br />\nFractional ownership optimizes the usage of upscale properties, enriching the ownership experience.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Evolving Property Management Practices</strong><br />\nProfessional property management relieves investors of day-to-day responsibilities, enhancing property value.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Impact on Traditional Real Estate Models</strong><br />\nThe rise of fractional ownership challenges traditional models, compelling adaptation for competitiveness.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Globalization of Real Estate Investment</strong><br />\nOnline platforms facilitate global diversification of portfolios, introducing a new dynamic to investment strategies.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>FAQs about Fractional Ownership</strong></h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>What is fractional ownership?</strong><br />\nFractional ownership involves multiple investors jointly owning a property, making high-value real estate accessible.</p>\n\n<p><strong>How does it differ from traditional ownership?</strong><br />\nTraditional ownership involves sole ownership, while fractional ownership allows multiple investors to share ownership.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What properties are suitable?</strong><br />\nFractional ownership applies to various properties, including residential, commercial, vacation, and luxury real estate.</p>\n\n<p><strong>How are decisions made?</strong><br />\nDecision-making depends on the ownership agreement, with clear communication and established protocols.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Can I sell my share?</strong><br />\nYes, fractional ownership offers potential liquidity, allowing investors to sell shares based on ownership terms.</p>\n\n<p><strong>How is rental income distributed?</strong><br />\nRental income distribution aligns with the ownership structure, managed by platforms or companies.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Are there risks?</strong><br />\nYes, fractional ownership carries inherent risks, mitigated by thorough due diligence and reputable platforms.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Are fractional ownership platforms regulated?</strong><br />\nRegulation varies, and investors should choose platforms adhering to legal frameworks for a secure environment.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Can I use my ownership for personal use?</strong><br />\nMany agreements allow personal use, with allocated time specified in the ownership agreement.</p>\n\n<p><strong>How do I get started?</strong><br />\nResearch reputable platforms, understand offerings, review agreements, and consult professionals for informed decision-making.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Case Study: Fractional Ownership in the Indian Real Estate Sector</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Background:</strong><br />\nIn the bustling city of Mumbai, India, renowned for its dynamic real estate market, a landmark residential project named &quot;Mumbai Residency&quot; introduced a pioneering approach to property ownership through fractional ownership. This development, valued at INR 200 million, sought to address the challenges of affordability and accessibility faced by potential investors in one of the country&#39;s most sought-after real estate markets.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Fractional Ownership Structure:</strong><br />\nA Mumbai-based real estate platform, &quot;IndiaShares,&quot; initiated the fractional ownership model for Mumbai Residency. The property was divided into 100,000 shares, with each share representing a portion of ownership. Interested investors could participate with an investment as low as INR 10,000, breaking down the traditional barriers to entry in the Mumbai real estate scene.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Investor Profile:</strong><br />\nIndiaShares attracted a diverse group of investors, including young professionals, expatriates, and seasoned investors looking to diversify their portfolios. The fractional ownership model appealed to those who aspired to own a piece of Mumbai&#39;s real estate market but found sole ownership financially challenging.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Advantages for Investors:</strong><br />\n<strong>Affordable Entry: </strong>The fractional ownership model allowed investors to enter the competitive Mumbai real estate market with a minimal investment, providing an opportunity for a more extensive demographic to participate.<br />\n<strong>Diversification:</strong> Investors leveraged fractional ownership to diversify their real estate holdings, spreading their investments across multiple properties to mitigate risk.<br />\n<strong>Potential Returns:</strong> As Mumbai Residency appreciated in value, investors experienced proportional returns. Rental income generated from leased units was distributed among shareholders based on their ownership percentage.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Management and Decision-Making:</strong><br />\nIndiaShares collaborated with a local property management company to oversee day-to-day operations, maintenance, and tenant interactions. Decision-making was facilitated through a digital platform, ensuring transparent communication and allowing shareholders to vote on key matters related to the property.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Challenges and Solutions:</strong><br />\n<strong>Regulatory Compliance: </strong>Negotiating India&#39;s complex regulatory landscape for real estate required IndiaShares to work closely with legal experts. Strict adherence to local laws ensured investor confidence and regulatory compliance.<br />\n<strong>Educational Initiatives: </strong>Recognizing the novelty of fractional ownership in India, IndiaShares invested in educational initiatives to inform potential investors about the model&#39;s benefits, risks, and legal aspects, fostering a greater understanding within the market.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Outcomes:</strong><br />\nThe fractional ownership model for Mumbai Residency proved successful. Investors enjoyed capital appreciation, received rental income, and experienced the pride of ownership in a prime Mumbai location. The project&#39;s success sparked interest from other developers and platforms, signaling a potential shift in the traditional real estate landscape.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Impact on the Indian Real Estate Market:</strong><br />\nIndiaShares&#39; fractional ownership model set a precedent in the Indian real estate market. The success of Mumbai Residency inspired other developers to explore similar models, promoting inclusivity and democratizing property ownership in a market known for its high entry barriers.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion:</strong><br />\nThis case study exemplifies how fractional ownership can address affordability challenges, open doors for a diverse investor base, and reshape the dynamics of the real estate market in India. As the concept gains acceptance and understanding, it has the potential to revolutionize the way properties are owned and invested in across the country.</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags_array":"","tags_commaseparted":"","published_time":1704672000,"published_date":"08 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1704777387,"date_format":"","date_time":"10:46 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"09 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"10:46 AM"},"updated_at":"Jan 09, 2024","updated_at_time":1704788576,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1704788586","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/GreenViews-Sample-House-A-Glimpse-into-Unparalleled-Living"},"id":282,"project_id":"35","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"GreenViews-Sample-House-A-Glimpse-into-Unparalleled-Living","image":"banner_1704454717_100.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1704454717_100.jpg","banner_title":"GreenView's Sample House: A Glimpse into Unparalleled Living","title":"GreenView's Sample House: A Glimpse into Unparalleled Living","description":"<p>We are thrilled to announce the recent launch of GreenView&#39;s sample house, a testament to our commitment to redefining modern living. With 80% of construction complete and an impressive 80% of units already sold out, GreenView is not just a development; it&#39;s a vision realized.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Setting a New Standard</strong></p>\n\n<p>GreenView&#39;s sample house isn&#39;t just a structure; it&#39;s an embodiment of our vision for unparalleled living. We&#39;ve meticulously curated every detail to showcase the unique features and benefits that set our project apart from the rest. From innovative design concepts to sustainable practices, our sample house is a tangible expression of the quality and lifestyle GreenView embodies.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Unparalleled Design</strong></p>\n\n<p>Step into the sample house, and you&#39;ll immediately sense the difference. Our design philosophy revolves around creating spaces that seamlessly blend aesthetics with functionality. The architecture embraces natural light, open spaces, and a harmonious connection with the surroundings. GreenView&#39;s sample house isn&#39;t just a home; it&#39;s a living experience designed for the modern homeowner.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Sustainable Living in Action</strong></p>\n\n<p>What truly distinguishes GreenView is our unwavering commitment to sustainability. The sample house serves as a living testament to our eco-friendly practices, featuring energy-efficient systems, water conservation initiatives, and the integration of green spaces. We believe in not just building homes but fostering a sustainable lifestyle for our residents.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Construction Milestone: 80% Complete</strong></p>\n\n<p>We are proud to announce that 80% of the construction at GreenView is now complete. This achievement is a testament to our dedication to delivering quality homes on time. As we move forward, the remaining construction will continue with the same level of precision and commitment, ensuring that every unit at GreenView is crafted to perfection. We are dedicated to completing the construction on time as the response to GreenView has been overwhelming, with 80% of the units already sold out. This incredible success speaks volumes about the appeal and desirability of our project. We extend our heartfelt thanks to those who have chosen GreenView as their future home. For those considering joining our community, now is the time to explore the remaining opportunities.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Community and Lifestyle<br />\nBeyond bricks and mortar, GreenView is about building a vibrant community and offering a lifestyle that reflects the aspirations of our residents. From recreational facilities to community spaces, we are shaping an environment where neighbours become friends, and every day brings new possibilities.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In conclusion, GreenView&#39;s sample house stands as a beacon of innovation, sustainability, and exceptional living. With 80% of construction completed and 80% of units sold out, GreenView is not just a development; it&#39;s a realization of a vision for a modern, sustainable, and vibrant community. We invite you to be a part of this extraordinary journey and discover the GreenView difference for yourself.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Bhavya Shah</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"GreenView's Sample House: A Glimpse into Unparalleled Living","seo_description":"Explore GreenView's sample house, a pinnacle of modern, sustainable living. Discover our innovative design, eco-friendly practices, and vibrant community. With 80% construction complete and units selling fast, join our vision for unparalleled living. Experience the GreenView difference in our state-of-the-art, sustainable sample house. Your future home awaits.","seo_keywords":"Greenview, Green Home, Shivalik, Adani Shantigram, Shivalik, Residential, Home, Real Estate, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1704455089_48.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1704455089_48.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Greenview","tag_lower":"greenview"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Shantigram","tag_lower":"shantigram"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Green Home","tag_lower":"green home"},{"text":"Residential","tag_lower":"residential"}],"tags_array":["Greenview","Shivalik","Shantigram","Real Estate","Green Home","Residential"],"tags_commaseparted":"Greenview,Shivalik,Shantigram,Real Estate,Green Home,Residential","published_time":1704393000,"published_date":"05 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1704454717,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:08 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"05 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"05:08 PM"},"updated_at":"Jan 05, 2024","updated_at_time":1704455089,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1704876189","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Why-is-Shivalik-Group-the-Best-Choice-for-NRI-Investors"},"id":278,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Why-is-Shivalik-Group-the-Best-Choice-for-NRI-Investors","image":"banner_1704257228_1.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1704257228_1.jpg","banner_title":"Why is Shivalik Group the Best Choice for NRI Investors?","title":"Why is Shivalik Group the Best Choice for NRI Investors?","description":"<p>Investing in real estate is always a smart choice and India presents unique opportunities for Non-Resident Indian (NRI) investors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With the rise of the Indian economy, NRIs are increasingly looking for opportunities to invest in India. The most important aspect is making a wise decision when choosing a developer to Invest with!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Group is a leading name in the real estate industry in Ahmedabad, offering NRIs a range of investment options ranging from affordable to ultra-luxurious properties.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With over 75 successful projects completed, the Shivalik Group has built a reputation for selecting prime locations that offer not only growth potential and accessibility, but also a track record of delivering high returns on investment for NRIs.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In this article, we will discuss more reasons why Shivalik Group is the wise choice for NRI investors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Transparency in Every Step</strong><br />\nShivalik Group prides itself on being transparent in the real estate industry. It is crucial for NRIs who manage investments from foreign locations to consider transparency as a key factor.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We ensure that every aspect of a project is accessible and understandable, from its conception to its completion.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Projects at Strategic Locations &amp; Upgrading Areas</strong><br />\nThe locations chosen for Shivalik Group projects are strategic and promising. NRIs often seek investments in areas with growth potential and accessibility, and Shivalik Group aligns perfectly with both of these factors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Upgraded locations are particularly appealing to NRIs as they offer modern amenities, infrastructure, and a higher standard of living. Shivalik Group&#39;s projects are conveniently located in such areas, making them an ideal choice for NRI investments.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Backward and Forward Integration</strong><br />\nBackwards and forward integration is a key strength of the Shivalik Group, as it includes S&amp;H, our construction company, and Lofy, our interior company.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This integration ensures seamless coordination and control over the entire construction process, from start to finish, resulting in high-quality projects that meet the expectations of NRI investors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Incorporating Sustainability for a Secure Future</strong><br />\nAs the global landscape evolves, so does the importance of sustainability in real estate. Shivalik Group is at the forefront of this trend, incorporating sustainable practices into its projects.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>NRIs can rest assured that their investment aligns with environmental consciousness and future-forward thinking.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Also read, Shivalik Group Delivers 1000 Green Homes This Festive Season!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Lifestyle Amenities Adding Value to Investments</strong><br />\nBeyond just the four walls, Shivalik Group integrates a wide range of amenities and lifestyle features into its projects.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>From state-of-the-art fitness centres to eco-friendly spaces, these additions not only attract potential tenants but also add significant value to the investment in the long run.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Providing 3D View &amp; Real-time Video Walkthrough</strong><br />\nShivalik Group offers 3D view video walkthroughs in these days when travel and physical visits can be challenging for NRIs.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>From the comfort of their homes, investors can explore every detail of the project. It saves time and gives you a realistic impression of the property as well.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Furthermore, Shivalik Group offers real time video updates of current projects and comprehensive details of each project to help clients make informed decisions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Convenient Pickup Drop Services</strong><br />\nA thoughtful gesture is offered by Shivalik Group to assist NRIs during visits - pickup and drop-off services.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In this way, inconveniences of transportation are removed during site visits. The Shivalik Group creates an environment where NRIs feel valued and cared for, beyond simply dealing with them.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The Iconic Buildings &amp; Architecture</strong><br />\nThe Shivalik Group takes pride in its iconic buildings and architectural designs. From modern office buildings to elegant residential complexes, the Shivalik Group&#39;s commitment to exceptional architecture sets it apart from other developers and ensures that NRIs can invest in properties that not only provide a comfortable living space but also become a source of pride and admiration.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Be Confident With Shivalik Group</strong><br />\nAre you ready to make your real estate investment with confidence? Find out more about Shivalik Group projects today and be part of something bigger.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Invest with Shivalik Group with confidence!</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Kishan Thakkar</span></p>\n","seo_title":"Why is Shivalik Group the Best Choice for NRI Investors?","seo_description":"Shivalik Group provides NRI investors with the best options for real estate investments in India. Invest with the leading industry experts and be assured of a safe and secure experience.","seo_keywords":"NRI, Real Estate, Investment, Shivalik, Ahmedabad, India","seo_image":"banner_1704257296_60.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1704257296_60.jpg","tags":[{"text":"NRI","tag_lower":"nri"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["NRI","Investment","Real Estate","Shivalik","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"NRI,Investment,Real Estate,Shivalik,Ahmedabad","published_time":1704220200,"published_date":"03 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1704257228,"date_format":"","date_time":"10:17 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"03 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"10:17 AM"},"updated_at":"Jan 03, 2024","updated_at_time":1704257296,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1704348672","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Greenovation-Unleashed-A-Paradigm-Shift-in-Sustainable-Living"},"id":277,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Greenovation-Unleashed-A-Paradigm-Shift-in-Sustainable-Living","image":"banner_1704101161_7.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1704101161_7.jpg","banner_title":"Greenovation Unleashed: A Paradigm Shift in Sustainable Living","title":"Greenovation Unleashed: A Paradigm Shift in Sustainable Living","description":"<p>In the dynamic landscape of sustainable living, we are excited to introduce our groundbreaking concept&mdash;&#39;Greenovation.&#39; This isn&#39;t just a new idea; it&#39;s a paradigm shift transcending traditional notions of green building and sustainability. Let&#39;s delve into what sets &#39;Greenovation&#39; apart and how it&#39;s poised to redefine the future of eco-conscious living.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Beyond Green Building: While green building practices have long been the cornerstone of sustainable development, Greenovation takes it further. It&#39;s a holistic approach that integrates innovation, technology, and community engagement to create living spaces that not only minimise environmental impact but actively contribute to a regenerative and thriving ecosystem.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Smart Sustainability: &#39;Greenovation&#39; embraces the synergy between smart technologies and sustainability. Our vision goes beyond energy-efficient lighting and recycled materials. Imagine homes that adapt to your lifestyle, optimising energy usage based on daily routines. &#39;Greenovation&#39; introduces a new era of homes that seamlessly integrate with the rhythm of modern living while minimising resource consumption.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Elevating Community Involvement: Sustainability is not just about structures; it&#39;s about fostering a sense of community. &#39;Greenovation&#39; places a strong emphasis on community involvement and collaboration. From shared green spaces to collaborative initiatives for waste reduction, our vision is to create communities where residents actively participate in the sustainability journey.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Regenerative Living Spaces: At the core of &#39;Greenovation&#39; is the concept of regenerative living. It&#39;s not just about lessening our environmental impact but actively contributing to the restoration of ecosystems. Imagine living in spaces where rainwater harvesting isn&#39;t just a feature but an integral part of a larger effort to replenish local water sources. &#39;Greenovation&#39; envisions homes that give back to the environment, creating a positive ecological footprint.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Interactive Sustainability Education: One of the unique aspects of &#39;Greenovation&#39; is the focus on interactive sustainability education. We believe that understanding the impact of our choices is key to fostering a sustainable mindset. From digital platforms offering real-time energy consumption insights to community workshops on eco-friendly practices, we aim to empower residents with the knowledge to make informed and sustainable decisions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Adapting to Changing Needs: The world is dynamic, and so are the needs of its inhabitants. &#39;Greenovation&#39; acknowledges this by creating spaces that adapt to changing lifestyles and environmental conditions. From modular designs that accommodate evolving family structures to the incorporation of resilient materials, our approach is to ensure that &#39;Greenovation&#39; isn&#39;t just a concept for today but a lasting solution for the future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&#39;Greenovation&#39; is more than a concept. It invites individuals to be active participants in the sustainability revolution. Whether you&#39;re a future resident, a community member, or an advocate for a greener future, &#39;Greenovation&#39; beckons you to join us on this transformative journey.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In conclusion, &#39;Greenovation&#39; isn&#39;t just a new idea; it&#39;s a commitment to redefining sustainable living. It&#39;s about embracing innovation, community collaboration, and regenerative practices. As we embark on this journey, we invite you to be part of &#39;Greenovation&#39;&mdash;where sustainability meets innovation, and every choice contributes to a brighter, greener future.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Bhavya Shah</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Greenovation Unleashed: A Paradigm Shift in Sustainable Living","seo_description":"Welcome to 'Greenovation'! A groundbreaking concept in sustainable living. Beyond traditional green building, it integrates innovation, technology, and community engagement to create spaces that actively contribute to a thriving ecosystem. Experience smart sustainability, regenerative living, and interactive education. 'Greenovation' adapts to evolving needs, ensuring a lasting solution. Join us in redefining eco-conscious living, where every choice leads to a brighter, greener future.","seo_keywords":"Innovation, Green, Green Homes, Sustainability, Shivalik, Green Innovation, Real Estate, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1704101336_84.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1704101336_84.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Green Homes","tag_lower":"green homes"},{"text":"Innovation","tag_lower":"innovation"},{"text":"Green Building","tag_lower":"green building"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Green Homes","Innovation","Green Building","Shivalik","Real Estate","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Green Homes,Innovation,Green Building,Shivalik,Real Estate,Ahmedabad","published_time":1704047400,"published_date":"01 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":1704101161,"date_format":"","date_time":"02:56 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"01 Jan, 2024","created_at_time":"02:56 PM"},"updated_at":"Jan 01, 2024","updated_at_time":1704101336,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1704174029","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Why-Investing-Now-in-Ahmedabad-Real-Estate-is-a-Wise-Choice-for-NRIs"},"id":276,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Why-Investing-Now-in-Ahmedabad-Real-Estate-is-a-Wise-Choice-for-NRIs","image":"banner_1703683631_41.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1703683631_41.jpg","banner_title":"Why Investing Now in Ahmedabad Real Estate is a Wise Choice for NRIs?","title":"Why Investing Now in Ahmedabad Real Estate is a Wise Choice for NRIs?","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>In recent years, Ahmedabad has emerged as a promising destination for real estate investment, offering a unique and highly profitable opportunity for Non-Resident Indians (NRIs).<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Real Estate in Ahmedabad is on the rise</strong><br />\nAhmedabad, the largest city in Gujarat, has witnessed a remarkable transformation in its real estate landscape in recent years.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The city&#39;s strategic location, well-developed infrastructure, and proactive government policies have fueled its real estate market, making it an attractive prospect for investors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In addition, the growth of infrastructure around Ahmedabad, such as GIFT City, Dholera expressway, Modi Stadium, etc, have made it the top choice for NRI investment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Economic Growth and Stability</strong><br />\nNRIs should look at Ahmedabad because of its consistent economic growth in industries such as textiles, pharmaceuticals, and information technology.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>According to recent statistics, Ahmedabad&#39;s GDP growth has consistently outpaced the national average, making it an economic powerhouse in its own right.</p>\n\n<p>The development of infrastructure around Ahmedabad, including initiatives like GIFT City, has further enhanced the city&#39;s appeal for NRI investors, creating a positive ripple effect on the real estate market.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Affordability and Diverse Investment Options</strong><br />\nCompared to other metropolitan cities like Mumbai and Bangalore, Ahmedabad offers a cost-effective real estate market. NRIs can capitalize on this affordability, gaining access to diverse investment options ranging from residential apartments to commercial spaces.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Read more on, Ahmedabad most affordable housing market, Mumbai most expensive: Knight Frank report</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Government Initiatives and Ease of Doing Business</strong><br />\nAhmedabad has consistently ranked high in terms of ease of doing business. Efforts by the local government to streamline bureaucratic processes have made investments both domestic and international more attractive.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The Real Estate (Regulation and Development) Act, 2016 (RERA) has also made the market more transparent and investor-friendly, thus providing more security to NRI investors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Conversion of currency is an advantage</strong><br />\nAnother significant factor for NRIs considering Ahmedabad real estate is the advantage gained through currency conversion rates. The favorable exchange rates can amplify returns on investment when converting foreign currency like Euro or Dollar into Indian Rupees.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This factor adds an extra layer of financial appeal, making Ahmedabad an even more appealing option for NRIs.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Cultural Centre and Attraction for People of All Lifestyles</strong><br />\nBeyond economic factors, Ahmedabad&#39;s rich cultural heritage like Pol House, and vibrant lifestyle add another layer of appeal. The city seamlessly blends tradition with modernity, offering a unique living experience.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This cultural richness contributes to the overall demand for real estate, making it an excellent choice for NRIs seeking both financial returns and a high-quality lifestyle.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Get The Best Returns With Ahmedabad Real Estate</strong><br />\nFor NRIs seeking to diversify their investment portfolios, Ahmedabad&#39;s real estate market offers a great opportunity. It has a high appreciation rate, affordability, favorable currency conversion, and a cultural attraction that sets it apart from other cities.</p>\n\n<p>Explore the possibilities of Ahmedabad real estate with Shivalik Group &ndash; Your Trusted Partner in Creating A Better Future.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Invest Smart, Invest in Ahmedabad!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">-&nbsp;Kishan Thakkar</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Why Investing in Ahmedabad Real Estate is a Wise Choice for NRIs?","seo_description":"Find out why Non-Resident Indian (NRI) investors should consider investing in Ahmedabad real estate. Learn why this city is a great place to invest in real estate.","seo_keywords":"Investment, NRI, India, Ahmedabad, Shivalik, Real Estate, Home","seo_image":"banner_1703683700_7.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1703683700_7.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"NRI","tag_lower":"nri"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"}],"tags_array":["Investment","NRI","Ahmedabad","Shivalik","GIFT City"],"tags_commaseparted":"Investment,NRI,Ahmedabad,Shivalik,GIFT City","published_time":1703615400,"published_date":"27 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1703683631,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:57 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"27 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"06:57 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 28, 2023","updated_at_time":1703743117,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1703743124","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Ahmedabads-Path-to-a-Greener-Tomorrow-Greenovation-by-Shivalik"},"id":274,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Ahmedabads-Path-to-a-Greener-Tomorrow-Greenovation-by-Shivalik","image":"banner_1703167713_70.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1703167713_70.jpg","banner_title":"Ahmedabad's Path to a Greener Tomorrow: Greenovation by Shivalik","title":"Ahmedabad's Path to a Greener Tomorrow: Greenovation by Shivalik","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>In a rapidly evolving world, the need for sustainable practices has become a necessity. Ahmedabad is a fast-growing metropolis in India. As the city continues to grow, the responsibility to maintain a harmonious balance between urban development and environmental well-being falls on the shoulders of conscientious leaders. Shivalik has risen to this challenge with its pioneering initiative: Greenovation.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Greenovation: A Commitment</strong></p>\n\n<p>Greenovation is not just a buzzword for Shivalik; it is a profound commitment to transforming the landscape of Ahmedabad, making it more sustainable, eco-conscious, and resilient. At its core, Greenovation embodies a vision where innovation helps urban development to coexist harmoniously with nature, creating a blueprint for a greener and more sustainable future for the city.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Beyond Traditional Real Estate:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s Greenovation goes beyond the conventional norms of real estate development. It is about taking a holistic approach, where every aspect of a project is designed and executed with a focus on environmental responsibility. From innovative building designs to sustainable materials and energy-efficient technologies, Shivalik is revolutionising the real estate sector.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Positive Impact on Ahmedabad:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik understands its role as a catalyst for positive change in Ahmedabad. Through Greenovation, the Shivalik is contributing significantly to the city&#39;s sustainable development:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Reduced Carbon Footprint</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik is reducing its carbon footprint by adopting green building practices. This translates into lower emissions and improved air quality, which benefits the entire city.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong></p>\n\n<p>Greenovation projects are designed with energy efficiency in mind. This not only reduces energy consumption but also helps homeowners save on their utility bills, making sustainable living more accessible to everyone.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Urban Aesthetics</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s projects are a testament to how urban aesthetics can seamlessly blend with natural surroundings. The cityscape is evolving into a more beautiful and environmentally conscious space.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Community Engagement</strong></p>\n\n<p>The Greenovation movement isn&#39;t just about structures; it&#39;s about fostering a sense of environmental responsibility within the community. Shivalik encourages residents, employees, and stakeholders to embrace green living practices, thus creating a ripple effect of positive change.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Economic Growth</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s investments in sustainable practices contribute to the growth of green industries and create jobs, bolstering the city&#39;s economic development.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s Greenovation is an initiative that demonstrates how responsible real estate development can positively impact a city&#39;s environment, economy, and quality of life. By taking this step towards sustainability, Shivalik is not just building structures; it&#39;s building a better future for Ahmedabad, where the city and nature bloom together.</p>\n","seo_title":"Ahmedabad's Path to a Greener Tomorrow: Greenovation by Shivalik","seo_description":"Explore Shivalik's Greenovation in Ahmedabad, a groundbreaking initiative blending urban development with environmental sustainability. This holistic approach revolutionizes real estate through eco-friendly designs, reduced carbon footprint, and community engagement. Greenovation is reshaping Ahmedabad's landscape, promoting energy efficiency and economic growth, while fostering a harmonious coexistence with nature.","seo_keywords":"Ahmedabad, Sustainability, Urban Development, Environment, Shivalik, Greenovation, Innovation, Sustainable Design","seo_image":"banner_1703167789_48.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1703167789_48.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Sustainability","tag_lower":"sustainability"},{"text":"Urban Development","tag_lower":"urban development"},{"text":"Environment","tag_lower":"environment"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Greenovation","tag_lower":"greenovation"},{"text":"Innovation","tag_lower":"innovation"},{"text":"Sustainable Design","tag_lower":"sustainable design"}],"tags_array":["Ahmedabad","Sustainability","Urban Development","Environment","Shivalik","Greenovation","Innovation","Sustainable Design"],"tags_commaseparted":"Ahmedabad,Sustainability,Urban Development,Environment,Shivalik,Greenovation,Innovation,Sustainable Design","published_time":1703097000,"published_date":"21 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1703167713,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:38 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"21 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"07:38 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 21, 2023","updated_at_time":1703167789,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1703574493","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/The-Green-Revolution-with-EV-Charging-Stations"},"id":272,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"The-Green-Revolution-with-EV-Charging-Stations","image":"banner_1702930693_45.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1702930693_45.jpg","banner_title":"The Green Revolution with EV Charging Stations","title":"The Green Revolution with EV Charging Stations","description":"<p>In the dynamic landscape of the automotive industry, electric vehicles (EVs) have swiftly emerged as the trendiest choice. Fueled by an escalating awareness of climate change and a widespread yearning for sustainable alternatives, EVs have experienced a remarkable surge in popularity. It is anticipated that by 2040, a staggering 57% of global passenger car sales will be electric, surpassing traditional internal combustion engine counterparts.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Future is Electric: Industry Statistics</strong><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Let&#39;s reflect on some compelling industry statistics that underscore the immense potential of EV charging stations:</p>\n\n<p>As of 2021, there are approximately 7 million public and private EV charging stations worldwide, with projections indicating a substantial increase in the coming years.</p>\n\n<p>The global electric vehicle charging infrastructure market is expected to reach an astounding $140 billion by 2030, exhibiting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 34%.<br />\nBy 2025, an estimated 13 million EV charging points will be available globally, driven by the escalating demand for electric vehicles.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Benefits of EV Points in Commercial Spaces:</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Diversified Revenue Streams:&nbsp;</strong><br />\nEV charging stations offer an excellent avenue for property owners to generate additional income. Whether through pay-per-use charging fees or collaborations with EV charging service providers, these stations can evolve into a reliable source of revenue.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Elevated Property Value:&nbsp;</strong><br />\nInstalling EV charging infrastructure can substantially boost the value of commercial properties. According to a recent study, properties equipped with EV charging stations command a premium of 7% or more compared to those without.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tenant Attraction and Retention:&nbsp;</strong><br />\nProviding EV charging stations as an amenity can be a game-changer in attracting and retaining tenants. With the increasing popularity of electric vehicles, renters and businesses are actively seeking properties that offer convenient charging options.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Marketing Advantage:&nbsp;</strong><br />\nEmbracing green initiatives such as EV charging infrastructure allows property owners to distinguish themselves from competitors and gain a marketing edge. It showcases a commitment to sustainability, resonating with an environmentally conscious consumer base.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Benefits of EV Points in Residential Spaces:</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Convenience Meets Sustainability</strong><br />\nBeyond the environmental impact, the integration of EV charging stations caters to the practical needs and aspirations of urban dwellers.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Picture this: you return home after a day&#39;s work, your electric vehicle seamlessly connects to the charging station in your building&#39;s parking lot, and you retire for the evening knowing that your car is not only recharging but doing so sustainably. It&#39;s a merge of convenience and eco-conscious living that resonates with the values of the modern, environmentally-aware homeowner.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Sustainable Living</strong><br />\nThe adoption of EV charging stations within residential complexes goes beyond individual choices; it transforms into a collective commitment to sustainable living. Communities that offer such facilities not only encourage residents to make greener choices but also contribute to reducing the carbon footprint of the entire neighborhood. It&#39;s a shared effort toward a more sustainable, environmentally responsible future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Economic Benefits</strong><br />\nInvesting in EV charging infrastructure is not just a gesture toward sustainability; it&#39;s a strategic move with economic benefits. As the demand for electric vehicles rises, properties equipped with EV charging stations become more attractive to potential homebuyers. This not only enhances property values but also positions these residences as forward-thinking, environmentally-conscious hubs in the real estate market.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Navigating the Technological Landscape</strong><br />\nThe integration of EV charging stations necessitates navigating the technological landscape. Smart charging solutions, integrated apps, and user-friendly interfaces are becoming integral aspects of residential charging infrastructure. Homeowners are not just plugging in; they are engaging with cutting-edge technology that aligns with their commitment to sustainable living.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>In Nutshell!</strong><br />\nEmbracing this shift toward eco-friendly urban living is not merely a choice; it&#39;s a responsibility we owe to our communities, our environment, and the generations to come. The surge of EV charging stations in residential buildings is a beacon of sustainable progress and a testament to our collective commitment to a greener, cleaner, and more sustainable urban lifestyle.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">-&nbsp;Jayshree Ochwani</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"The Green Revolution with EV Charging Stations","seo_description":"Discover the future of urban living with the Green Revolution in EV Charging Stations. As electric vehicles surge in popularity, witness the economic benefits in commercial and residential spaces. From diversified revenue streams to sustainable living, it's a collective commitment for a greener, cleaner, and more sustainable urban lifestyle. Embrace the responsibility of a brighter tomorrow.","seo_keywords":"Sustainability, EV, EV, Charging Station, Going green, Green initiative, Shivalik, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1702930823_7.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1702930823_7.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Sustainable","tag_lower":"sustainable"},{"text":"EV Charging Stations","tag_lower":"ev charging stations"},{"text":"Commercial","tag_lower":"commercial"},{"text":"Residential","tag_lower":"residential"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"}],"tags_array":["Sustainable","EV Charging Stations","Commercial","Residential","Shivalik"],"tags_commaseparted":"Sustainable,EV Charging Stations,Commercial,Residential,Shivalik","published_time":1702924200,"published_date":"19 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1702930693,"date_format":"","date_time":"01:48 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"19 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"01:48 AM"},"updated_at":"Dec 19, 2023","updated_at_time":1702930823,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1703066549","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Color-Psychology-in-Interior-Design"},"id":271,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"8","slug":"Color-Psychology-in-Interior-Design","image":"banner_1702642123_67.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1702642123_67.jpeg","banner_title":"Color Psychology in Interior Design","title":"Color Psychology in Interior Design","description":"<p>Choosing the right color palette for your home is crucial in interior design as colors can significantly impact mood and atmosphere. Understanding color psychology helps create spaces that align with your preferences and desired ambience.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Start by considering the primary function of each room. For example, calming tones like blues and greens are ideal for bedrooms, promoting relaxation and restful sleep. In contrast, vibrant hues such as yellows and oranges work well in areas meant for socializing, like the living room, fostering energy and warmth.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Neutral colors like beige, grey, and white serve as versatile foundations, allowing you to experiment with accent colors. They create a timeless backdrop and offer flexibility for changing styles or preferences over time.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Warm colors like reds and yellows can add coziness and intimacy to a space, making them suitable for dining rooms or areas where you want to encourage conversation. However, it&#39;s essential to balance warm tones with cooler ones to prevent the space from feeling too intense.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Cool colors, such as blues and greens, evoke a sense of calmness and tranquillity. These are excellent choices for spaces where relaxation is a priority, like bathrooms or reading nooks. Various shades within the cool color spectrum can add depth and interest to the design.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Consider the size and lighting of each room. Lighter colors can make a small room feel more spacious, while darker hues create a more intimate atmosphere in larger spaces. Pay attention to natural light, as it can influence how colors appear throughout the day.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Texture plays a role in color perception as well. Matte finishes absorb more light, giving colors a softer appearance, while glossy finishes reflect light, making colors more vibrant. Experimenting with textures can enhance the overall visual appeal of your chosen color palette.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Harmony is key when combining colors. Analogous color schemes involve selecting colors that are adjacent on the color wheel, creating a cohesive and serene look. Complementary color schemes involve pairing colors from opposite sides of the wheel, providing high contrast and vibrancy.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Don&#39;t overlook the psychological impact of neutrals. White signifies purity and cleanliness, making it a popular choice for bathrooms and kitchens. Beige is associated with warmth and stability, making it a versatile option for various rooms.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Bold accent colors can be introduced through accessories, artwork, or furniture. This allows you to inject personality into your space without committing to an entire room painted in a bold hue. Consider the emotional response you want to evoke when choosing these accents.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Ultimately, personal preferences should guide your color choices. Your home reflects your style and personality, so choose colors that resonate with you. Sample paint colors in small sections of the wall to see how they interact with the room&#39;s lighting before committing to a full application.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Hence, color psychology is a powerful tool in interior design. By understanding the emotional and visual impact of different colors, you can create a home that not only looks appealing but also supports the desired atmosphere for each room.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-Hardi Shah</span><br />\n&nbsp;</h5>\n","seo_title":"Choosing the right color palette","seo_description":"Understanding color psychology helps create spaces that align with your preferences and desired ambience. Choose the right color palette for your home","seo_keywords":"Interior ideas, home color, colors","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags_array":"","tags_commaseparted":"","published_time":1702578600,"published_date":"15 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1702642123,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:38 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"15 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"05:38 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 15, 2023","updated_at_time":1702642489,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1702643200","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Going-green-today-for-the-greener-tomorrow"},"id":270,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Going-green-today-for-the-greener-tomorrow","image":"banner_1702555674_66.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1702555674_66.jpg","banner_title":"Going green today for the greener tomorrow","title":"Going green today for the greener tomorrow","description":"<p>In the dynamic world of real estate, blending green initiatives with innovative practices is becoming a game-changer for a more sustainable future. Numerous studies emphasize the pivotal role that eco-friendly practices and inventive approaches play in the real estate sector. According to a report by the World Green Building Council, buildings designed with sustainability in mind not only contribute to environmental preservation but also enhance the well-being of those who inhabit them. The Global ESG Real Estate Report reveals a rising trend in investor preference, with a growing demand for environmentally conscious properties. As awareness of environmental concerns increases, the fusion of green and innovative practices is not just a choice; it&#39;s a necessity.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik, a pioneer in this movement, champions the concept of &quot;Greenovation,&quot; where each project seamlessly integrates sustainable design with innovation, setting a new standard for responsible and forward-thinking real estate development.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Research and Markets predict a bright future for the global green building market, projecting a substantial growth of 10.26% by 2024. The effectiveness of green buildings is remarkable, evidenced by a proven reduction in energy consumption by up to 30% and water usage by 11%, according to the U.S. Green Building Council. Additionally, the World Green Building Council asserts that integrating sustainable practices in real estate significantly contributes to lowering greenhouse gas emissions, positively impacting the global fight against climate change. These statistics highlight the concrete advantages of Greenovation in reshaping the real estate landscape towards a more sustainable and resilient future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Incorporating green initiatives is not just an environmental effort; it&#39;s a smart move with economic and social benefits. The use of energy-efficient technologies, sustainable construction materials, and waste reduction not only lessens the environmental impact but also significantly cuts down on operational costs in the long term. A study by the Urban Land Institute highlights that green building features, like improved indoor air quality and energy efficiency, contribute to increased property values and tenant satisfaction. Greenovation isn&#39;t just a passing trend; it&#39;s a transformative approach that recognises the interplay between human habitats and the natural world.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The synergy of innovation and sustainability is evident in the distinct projects undertaken by Shivalik. From harnessing renewable energy sources to designing spaces prioritising natural light and ventilation, Shivalik&#39;s commitment to Greenovation showcases the company&#39;s foresight and responsibility. By aligning with global sustainability goals and leveraging cutting-edge technologies, Shivalik aims to leave a lasting positive impact on the environment while creating spaces that foster the well-being of its occupants. In a world where the call for sustainable development grows louder, Greenovation in real estate emerges as a guiding light, offering a roadmap for a future where progress and responsibility go hand in hand.</p>\n","seo_title":"Going green today for the greener tomorrow","seo_description":"Discover the transformative synergy of green initiatives and innovation in real estate with Shivalik's pioneering concept, \"Greenovation.\" Addressing environmental concerns and societal well-being, explore how this forward-thinking approach reshapes the industry. Dive into impactful statistics revealing the tangible benefits, projecting a sustainable and resilient future where progress and responsibility coexist.","seo_keywords":"Greenovation Sustainable real estate Innovation Environmental preservation Green building Energy-efficient technologies Shivalik Sustainable development","seo_image":"banner_1702555718_45.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1702555718_45.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Greenhomes","tag_lower":"greenhomes"},{"text":"Sustainability","tag_lower":"sustainability"},{"text":"Homes","tag_lower":"homes"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Greenovation","tag_lower":"greenovation"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Greenhomes","Sustainability","Homes","Shivalik","Greenovation","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Greenhomes,Sustainability,Homes,Shivalik,Greenovation,Ahmedabad","published_time":1702492200,"published_date":"14 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1702555675,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:37 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"14 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"05:37 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 14, 2023","updated_at_time":1702555718,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1702619898","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/The-Thought-Process-Behind-the-Curv-of-India"},"id":269,"project_id":"175","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"The-Thought-Process-Behind-the-Curv-of-India","image":"banner_1702285465_18.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1702285465_18.jpg","banner_title":"The Thought Process Behind the Curv of India","title":"The Thought Process Behind the Curv of India","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>In the heart of GIFT City, where architectural wonders grace the skyline, Shivalik unveils its latest masterpiece &ndash; Curv. This iconic project has emerged as a beacon of challenge and creativity, setting a new benchmark in India&#39;s financial hub.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Glimpse of GIFT City&#39;s Beauty</strong></p>\n\n<p>Having kicked off four successful projects in GIFT City, we couldn&#39;t help but marvel at the captivating buildings that surround this bustling financial district. The idea of Curv germinated from our desire to not just create another structure but to craft a unique presence in GIFT&#39;s remarkable landscape.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>An uninterrupted view</strong></p>\n\n<p>Curv&#39;s strategic location offers an unparalleled panoramic view of the entire skyline. With riverfront and skyline vistas, Curv stands as a testament to our commitment to providing a unique experience for our clients. We wanted to cover both aspects &ndash; the grandeur of the riverfront and the urban charm of the skyline.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Inspiration from Nature: The Sea Shell Twist</strong></p>\n\n<p>The idea took shape as we observed the intricate twists of a sea shell, a beautiful phenomenon where each layer gracefully spirals. This inspiration led us to conceptualise a tower that reflects the same elegance. Curv, with its twisting silhouette, stands as the first of its kind in India.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Challenges in the Journey</strong></p>\n\n<p>The planning phase brought numerous challenges, but we embraced each one to ensure the final product surpassed expectations. The strategic placement of offices with wide-angle views showcases the beauty of GIFT City, providing a refreshing atmosphere within the building.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Crafting a Lively Environment Inside</strong></p>\n\n<p>Understanding the importance of a lively workspace, we incorporated an expansive atrium. This not only enhances the visual appeal but also ensures a vibrant and refreshing ambience that directly influences productivity.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>An Iconic Landmark: Curv</strong></p>\n\n<p>The culmination of meticulous planning and attention to detail resulted in an awe-inspiring structure. Visitors and onlookers alike acknowledge the beauty that is Curv. Our clients at Curv, both staff and owners, take pride in having an office within this architectural marvel.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Thought Process of India&#39;s Curv</strong></p>\n\n<p>Every twist and turn in the planning process, the challenges faced, and the intricate details considered have given birth to Curv &ndash; a testament to Shivalik&#39;s commitment to Innovation and excellence towards landmarks.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Commercial Landmark of India</strong></p>\n\n<p>Curv is not just a structure; it&#39;s a thoughtfully crafted space that defies norms. Even a 20-page article wouldn&#39;t suffice to cover all the intricacies and challenges encountered in creating Curv. Curv &ndash; an icon that stands tall in GIFT City, a testament to Shivalik&#39;s pursuit of iconic landmarks.</p>\n","seo_title":"Decoding Curv: Shivalik's Commercial Landmark Of India","seo_description":"Discover the thought process shaping the iconic Curv in the heart of GIFT City. Shivalik's latest masterpiece transcends conventional architecture, drawing inspiration from nature's sea shell twists. Overcoming challenges, Curv stands as India's commercial landmark, offering a unique blend of panoramic views, vibrant interiors, and a testament to Shivalik's commitment to innovation and excellence.","seo_keywords":"Curv, Shivalik, Landmark, Commercial Landmark, GIFT City, Ahmedabad, Shivalik","seo_image":"banner_1702285683_20.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1702285683_20.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Curv","tag_lower":"curv"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Landmark","tag_lower":"landmark"},{"text":"Commercial","tag_lower":"commercial"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"}],"tags_array":["Curv","Shivalik","Landmark","Commercial","GIFT City","Ahmedabad","India"],"tags_commaseparted":"Curv,Shivalik,Landmark,Commercial,GIFT City,Ahmedabad,India","published_time":1702233000,"published_date":"11 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1702285465,"date_format":"","date_time":"02:34 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"11 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"02:34 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 11, 2023","updated_at_time":1702285683,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1702300881","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Things-to-Keep-in-Mind-When-Investing-in-a-Luxury-Apartment"},"id":266,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Things-to-Keep-in-Mind-When-Investing-in-a-Luxury-Apartment","image":"banner_1701951665_27.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701951665_27.jpg","banner_title":"Things to Keep in Mind When Investing in a Luxury Apartment","title":"Things to Keep in Mind When Investing in a Luxury Apartment","description":"<p>Dreaming of owning a lavish villa or investing in a high-end luxury apartment is a common aspiration. While deciding to indulge in a luxurious living space is exciting, evaluating whether the property is truly worth its premium can be challenging.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Once the decision is made to invest in a luxury apartment, it is crucial to consider a few key factors:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Location, Location, Location</strong><br />\nThe foremost consideration when purchasing a luxury apartment is its location. The setting of the complex plays a pivotal role in determining accessibility to essential social infrastructure such as educational institutions, medical facilities, entertainment, and social avenues. Interacting with neighbours can provide insights into the sense of community. A well-chosen location is often reflected in the property&#39;s pricing.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Form, Function, Finish</strong><br />\nAttention to detail by the developer should be noticed in pursuing a luxury apartment. Beyond the visual appeal, ensuring that the property adheres to the National Building Code, particularly its resilience to natural disasters like earthquakes, is imperative. Quality luxury fittings, including climate control systems, solar panels, and rainwater harvesting systems, should match the financial investment. The construction techniques, material quality, and premium finishes reveal the true essence of luxury.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Technology</strong><br />\nLuxury apartments are designed to offer maximum comfort and cutting-edge facilities. Features such as landscaped gardens, spacious living areas, fully equipped kitchens, Wi-Fi, automated temperature control, and in-house gyms are common in upscale residential projects. Ensuring the chosen luxury apartment incorporates the latest technology and amenities is essential.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Security</strong><br />\nHigh-value luxury apartments often feature smart and technologically advanced security systems. Whether discreet security cameras, automated alarm systems, or access control systems for monitoring visitor entry, these measures ensure the home&#39;s and its residents&#39; safety.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Group is a noteworthy option for those seeking a genuine luxury home in Ahmedabad. As one of India&#39;s finest luxury real estate brands, Shivalik Group is renowned for its leadership and excellence in real estate development. Their approach focuses on planned development, creating valuable assets, and offering unforgettable lifestyle experiences through smart design and innovative architecture.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5>-&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-006642bf-7fff-4a6d-806a-0ee41f205cc9\">&nbsp;</b>Khushbu Raval</span></h5>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n","seo_title":"Unlocking Opulence: A Guide to Smart Luxury Apartment Investments Revealed by Shivalik Group","seo_description":"Discover the crucial factors to consider when investing in a luxury apartment, ensuring your dream home matches its premium value.","seo_keywords":"Luxury Apartment Investments, Real Estate Investment, High-End Living, Luxury Property Tips, Premium Real Estate, Smart Investment Choices","seo_image":"banner_1701951737_10.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701951737_10.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Residential","tag_lower":"residential"},{"text":"Apartment","tag_lower":"apartment"},{"text":"Luxury Apartment","tag_lower":"luxury apartment"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"}],"tags_array":["Residential","Apartment","Luxury Apartment","Real Estate","Ahmedabad","Shivalik"],"tags_commaseparted":"Residential,Apartment,Luxury Apartment,Real Estate,Ahmedabad,Shivalik","published_time":1701887400,"published_date":"07 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1701951665,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:51 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"07 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"05:51 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 07, 2023","updated_at_time":1701951737,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1702014264","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Shivalik-Groups-Vision-for-the-Future-of-Real-Estate-in-India"},"id":262,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Shivalik-Groups-Vision-for-the-Future-of-Real-Estate-in-India","image":"banner_1701785941_24.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701785941_24.jpg","banner_title":"Shivalik Group’s Vision for the Future of Real Estate in India","title":"Shivalik Group’s Vision for the Future of Real Estate in India","description":"<p>In the dynamic of Indian real estate, the Shivalik Group has become a participant and a visionary leader, minting a path towards a future where real estate development harmonizes with environmental sustainability and innovative design. Their commitment to integrating green building practices, innovative architectural designs, and strategic locations speaks volumes about their dedication to being a change for modern India.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This blog aims to publicize the ambitious vision of the Shivalik Group. Some key points behind <strong>Shivalik Group&rsquo;s Vision</strong> for the Future of Real Estate in India are as follows:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>1. Green Building and Sustainable Environments</strong></p>\n\n<p>At the heart of Shivalik Group&#39;s ethos is a commitment to green building practices. Understanding how critical sustainable development is, the Group blends eco-friendly designs and materials in its projects. This approach is about reducing the environmental footprint and creating healthier living spaces for residents. From energy-efficient lighting to water-saving fixtures and renewable materials, every aspect of a project is designed with sustainability.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>2. Cost-Effective Living through Low Maintenance</strong></p>\n\n<p>Sustainability surpasses environmental benefits; Green buildings are inherently low-maintenance, translating into significant cost savings for residents. Green buildings are significantly lower than traditional structures, offering long-term financial benefits to homeowners.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>3. Crafting a Better Skyline with Innovative Designs</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s projects are a testament to innovative architectural design in transforming city skylines. These buildings add to the urban landscape&#39;s aesthetic appeal and serve as icons and functional facilities. These projects showcase their dedication to creating exceptional designs that merge functionality with visual elegance.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>4. Redefining GIFT City&#39;s Skyline with Shivalik Skyview and Shivalik Curv</strong></p>\n\n<p>In the quest to define the Gujarat International Finance Tec-City (GIFT) skyline, Shivalik is working on two marquee projects: Shivalik Skyview and Shivalik Curv. These projects are thought to be landmarks of innovation with ultra-modern facilities. The Group aims to create architectural marvels that set new urban development standards. Other than these, Shivalik Highstreet and Shivalik Shilp are perfect examples of the Group&#39;s vision brought to life. They are premium commercial hubs symbolising profound working experience with architectural excellence and comfortable space.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>5. Prime Locations for Discerning Customers</strong></p>\n\n<p>Location is paramount in real estate, and Shivalik meticulously chooses prime locales for their projects. Their properties are strategically situated in areas offering the best urban living &mdash; from essential services to leisure and entertainment options.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In conclusion, Shivalik&rsquo;s vision for the future of real estate in India is a harmonious blend of sustainability, innovation, and community-focused development. They have established an ecosystem that provides a better standard of living, financial gains, and a feeling of community rather than merely buildings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">-&nbsp;Nidhi Raikundaliya</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Shivalik Group’s Vision for the Future of Real Estate in India","seo_description":"Shivalik Group is an Indian real estate company that focuses on sustainable building practices, innovative architectural designs, and strategic locations. They aim to reduce environmental impact, create healthier living spaces, and offer cost-effective living. They are working on defining the Gujarat International Finance Tec-City skyline and strategically placing properties in essential areas.","seo_keywords":"Real Estate, Vision, Shivalik, Homes, Sustainability","seo_image":"banner_1701786103_62.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701786103_62.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Vision","tag_lower":"vision"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Sustainability","tag_lower":"sustainability"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Shivalik","Vision","Ahmedabad","Sustainability"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Shivalik,Vision,Ahmedabad,Sustainability","published_time":1701714600,"published_date":"05 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1701785941,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:49 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"05 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"07:49 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 05, 2023","updated_at_time":1701786103,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701853537","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Shivalik-Group-Delivers-1000-Green-Homes-This-Festive-Season"},"id":259,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Shivalik-Group-Delivers-1000-Green-Homes-This-Festive-Season","image":"banner_1701690349_94.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701690349_94.jpeg","banner_title":"1000 Green Homes Delivered","title":"Shivalik Group Delivers 1000 Green Homes This Festive Season!","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>The Shivalik Group is making history by delivering 1000 green homes this festive season. This is not only a major milestone for us, but it is also a remarkable achievement for sustainability and green living.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Shivalik Group&#39;s Four &#39;Green&#39; Projects</strong>:<br />\nThese projects are a part of Shivalik Group&rsquo;s larger commitments to green living, which includes these four projects that are focused on promoting green practices.</p>\n\n<p>The four projects &mdash;Shivalik Parkview 2 in Shela, Shivalik Edge on Ambli-Bopal Road, Shivalik Platinum on Judges Bunglow Road, and Shivalik Enclave in Shahibaug&mdash;have received the necessary BU permissions, marking a significant step towards the fulfilment of the homebuyers&#39; dreams.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Each of the four projects has been recognized and certified by the Indian Green Building Council (IGBC).</p>\n\n<p><br />\nAdditionally, all of the projects are well-connected to the city&#39;s many transit points, allowing for easy access to the city&#39;s many attractions. These projects will appeal to homebuyers seeking a comfortable and convenient lifestyle due to their wide range of features.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWhy Ahmedabad Needs More Green Homes?<br />\nGreen homes are more important than ever, especially in cities like Ahmedabad where rapid development is putting a strain on the environment.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The use of green homes can help reduce air pollution, conserve water, reduce electricity bills, and improve air and water quality.</p>\n\n<p>Our green homes aim to provide a healthier, more comfortable living environment for homebuyers, while also promoting eco-friendly practices that will benefit the local community and environment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Features and Amenities of Our Green Homes</strong>:<br />\nThe Shivalik Group is not only focused on providing green homes but also on creating an eco-friendly living experience for its residents.</p>\n\n<p>All the buildings are equipped with the latest amenities, such as solar panels, rainwater harvesting, and wastewater treatment facilities. These features not only help reduce the overall environmental impact but also help to reduce energy costs in the long run.</p>\n\n<p>Additionally, the projects have been designed to maximize natural light and ventilation, making them more comfortable and energy-efficient. Shivalik Group has also taken special measures to ensure the security of its residents, with a multi-level security system in place.</p>\n\n<p>From well-manicured gardens to vibrant children&#39;s play areas and fully-equipped clubhouses, every project is designed with the resident&#39;s lifestyle in mind.</p>\n\n<p>Enjoy a Greener and More Sustainable Living Experience with Shivalik Group.<br />\nThe possession of these homes not only fulfills a dream but also marks the beginning of a new chapter for homeowners.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nShivalik Group, with 25 years of strong presence in the real estate industry, has successfully delivered over 8,000 units across 75 residential and commercial projects. This track record is proof of the trust and satisfaction of its customers.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nLooking ahead, we plan to continue this journey by handing over an additional 500 homes by mid-2024, further enriching the lives of the people of Ahmedabad.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nIt&#39;s time to move into your green home!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-Kishan Thakkar</span>&nbsp;</h5>\n","seo_title":"Shivalik Group Delivers 1000 Green Homes This Festive Season!","seo_description":"Shivalik Group is achieving another milestone by delivering 1000 green homes in Ahmedabad this festive season. Getting to this milestone is a major step forward for green and sustainable living.","seo_keywords":"Green Building, Shivalik Group, Sustainability, Shivalik","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Green Building","tag_lower":"green building"}],"tags_array":["Green Building"],"tags_commaseparted":"Green Building","published_time":1701628200,"published_date":"04 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1701690349,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:15 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"04 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"05:15 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 04, 2023","updated_at_time":1701691128,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"153","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701691139","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Riti Pancholi","added_by_type":"article manager"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Elevate-Your-Lofy-Experience-Balcony-Decoration-Ideas"},"id":258,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"8","slug":"Elevate-Your-Lofy-Experience-Balcony-Decoration-Ideas","image":"banner_1701691743_97.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701691743_97.jpeg","banner_title":"Elevate Your Lofy Experience: Balcony Decoration Ideas","title":"Elevate Your Lofy Experience: Balcony Decoration Ideas","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>A well-designed balcony can be a sanctuary, offering fresh air and a place to relax amidst the hustle and bustle of urban life. With the interiors of Lofy by Shivalik Group in your home, you have the perfect canvas to create a stunning outdoor space. With a little creativity and some thoughtful planning, you can transform your balcony into a charming oasis that complements the modern aesthetic of your Lofy residence.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Choose the Right Furniture</strong></p>\n\n<p>The first step in balcony decoration is selecting the right furniture. Opt for comfortable and space-saving pieces like foldable chairs, a small table, or a cosy outdoor sofa. Consider weather-resistant materials like rattan, teak, or metal to ensure durability.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Add Greenery</strong></p>\n\n<p>Plants are the heart and soul of any outdoor space. Consider a mix of potted plants, hanging planters, and vertical gardens to infuse your balcony with lush greenery. Choose plants that thrive in your local climate and suit outdoor conditions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Create Ambiance with Lighting</strong></p>\n\n<p>A well-planned lighting scheme can transform your balcony into a magical retreat, especially in the evening. String lights, lanterns, and candles can add a warm and inviting glow. Solar-powered lights are an eco-friendly choice that requires minimal maintenance.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Incorporate Comfortable Textiles</strong></p>\n\n<p>Enhance the comfort of your balcony with plush cushions, throw pillows, and cosy blankets. Opt for fabrics that are designed for outdoor use, as they are weather-resistant and easy to clean.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Define Your Style</strong></p>\n\n<p>Consider the overall aesthetic of your Lofy apartment and extend it to your balcony. Whether you prefer a minimalist, bohemian, or contemporary look, choose decor and accessories that reflect your style.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Maximise Space with Multi-functional Furniture</strong></p>\n\n<p>If your balcony is smaller, make the most of the space with multi-functional furniture. Look for items that serve dual purposes, such as storage benches or tables with built-in planters.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Create Privacy</strong></p>\n\n<p>Depending on your location, you might want to add privacy to your balcony. Use tall plants, bamboo screens, or outdoor curtains to create a secluded and intimate atmosphere.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Maintain a Clutter-Free Space</strong></p>\n\n<p>Lastly, keep your balcony tidy and organised. Avoid overcrowding the space with too much furniture or decor. A clutter-free environment will help you fully enjoy the beauty of your outdoor retreat.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In conclusion, decorating your balcony is an opportunity to create a tranquil escape outside your door, with Lofy by Shivalik Group, you can create exclusive and functional designs. It can be the perfect cosy corner of your house to read books with a warm cup of coffee during the cold weather.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For more information about Lofy apartments and interior solutions, visit https://www.shivalikgroup.com/lofy--interior-solution&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-&nbsp;<meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-bf5c2673-7fff-450f-2ce8-5a4fe20974a9\">Khushbu Raval</b></span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Transform Your Lofy Balcony: Expert Decoration Ideas for a Stylish Outdoor Retreat","seo_description":"Discover expert tips to elevate your Lofy balcony experience. Create a serene outdoor sanctuary amidst urban life with these innovative decoration ideas. Learn to choose the right furniture, incorporate lush greenery, set the perfect ambience with lighting, and more.","seo_keywords":"Lofy apartment, Shivalik Group, balcony decor, outdoor space, urban oasis, weather-resistant furniture, greenery, ambient lighting, comfortable textiles, multi-functional furniture, privacy solutions, art and decor, water feature, clutter-free space","seo_image":"banner_1701755881_56.jpeg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701755881_56.jpeg","tags":[{"text":"Interior","tag_lower":"interior"},{"text":"Home","tag_lower":"home"},{"text":"Home garden","tag_lower":"home garden"},{"text":"Balcony","tag_lower":"balcony"},{"text":"Interior Design","tag_lower":"interior design"},{"text":"Lofy","tag_lower":"lofy"}],"tags_array":["Interior","Home","Home garden","Balcony","Interior Design","Lofy"],"tags_commaseparted":"Interior,Home,Home garden,Balcony,Interior Design,Lofy","published_time":1701801000,"published_date":"06 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":1701668660,"date_format":"","date_time":"11:14 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"04 Dec, 2023","created_at_time":"11:14 AM"},"updated_at":"Dec 06, 2023","updated_at_time":1701853784,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701853803","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/The-Real-Estate-Industry-is-Thriving-in-India"},"id":255,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"The-Real-Estate-Industry-is-Thriving-in-India","image":"banner_1701301119_37.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701301119_37.jpg","banner_title":"The Real Estate Industry is Thriving in India!","title":"The Real Estate Industry is Thriving in India!","description":"<p>Real estate has always been a reliable and profitable investment option. But what&#39;s the secret behind its constant growth? Whether it&#39;s the house you call home or the towering skyscrapers in the city center, real estate isn&#39;t just bricks and mortar&ndash;it&#39;s a source of substantial wealth for many.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2><br />\nFactors Fueling the Real Estate Boom</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Urbanization and Economic Expansion</strong></p>\n\n<p>The real estate boom in India owes its success to several key factors, including urbanization, technological advancements, economic growth, government initiatives, and evolving business trends. The real estate sector is experiencing high demand across residential, commercial, and retail segments, primarily due to increased investments in infrastructure, favorable policies, and rising income levels. This growth is closely linked to corporate demand and urbanization, which, in turn, creates economic opportunities and jobs.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Government Initiatives and Foreign Investments</strong></p>\n\n<p>Government initiatives like &quot;Make in India&quot; and foreign direct investments (FDI) have played a significant role in improving infrastructure and attracting foreign capital to the real estate sector, propelling its growth.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Technological Advancements</strong></p>\n\n<p>The digital transformation has revolutionized the real estate industry, increasing the demand for flexible and technologically advanced office spaces, particularly in the commercial real estate sector. Businesses now seek cutting-edge, tech-enabled office spaces, further boosting the real estate market.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Growth Projections</strong></p>\n\n<p>India&#39;s real estate market is set to achieve remarkable milestones. It&#39;s estimated to contribute around 13% to the country&#39;s GDP by 2025 and is on track to become a $1 trillion market by 2030. This rapid growth is driven by urbanization, rising incomes, increased investments, and a growing preference for secure and lucrative real estate investments, both in residential and commercial properties.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Demographics</strong></p>\n\n<p>Demographic factors such as age, gender, and income levels have a substantial impact on property prices and preferences. For example, the retirement of the baby boomer generation is driving the demand for second homes in picturesque locations, while smaller households due to children moving out are increasing the appeal of cozy cottages.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Interest Rates</strong></p>\n\n<p>Interest rates play a critical role in the real estate market. Low-interest rates make mortgages more affordable, attracting more buyers and pushing property prices higher. Conversely, high-interest rates can dampen demand, leading to a decrease in real estate values.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Economic Considerations</strong></p>\n\n<p>The overall economic health of a nation significantly influences real estate asset valuations. Economic indicators like GDP, employment data, manufacturing activity, and price levels have a direct impact on market activity. Different real estate categories respond differently to economic cycles, with properties like hotels being more sensitive to economic downturns compared to office spaces due to lease structures.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Government Policies</strong></p>\n\n<p>Government policies and interventions have a substantial influence on real estate demand and pricing dynamics. Fiscal incentives, tax credits, deductions, and subsidies can stimulate or restrain demand for real estate assets, thus shaping market trends.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Investment Strategies</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investors have a choice between direct and indirect approaches to real estate investment. Direct ownership of physical properties or indirect strategies like Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs) and Exchange-Traded Funds (ETFs) offer distinct advantages regarding risk exposure, potential rewards, and market accessibility.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>As you embark on your investment journey, take the time to study these elements&ndash;it&#39;s an investment in itself and ensures that your decision-making process is well-informed.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">-&nbsp;Jayshree Ochwani</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"The Real Estate Industry is Thriving in India","seo_description":"India's real estate boom is fueled by urbanization, economic expansion, government initiatives, and evolving business trends. High demand across residential, commercial, and retail segments is driven by infrastructure investments, favorable policies, and rising income. The market is expected to contribute 13% to GDP by 2025 and $1 trillion by 2030.","seo_keywords":"Real Estate, Development, Shivalik, Ahmedabad, India","seo_image":"banner_1701301216_55.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701301216_55.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"},{"text":"Development","tag_lower":"development"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Shivalik","Ahmedabad","India","Development"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Shivalik,Ahmedabad,India,Development","published_time":1701282600,"published_date":"30 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1701301120,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:08 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"30 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"05:08 AM"},"updated_at":"Nov 30, 2023","updated_at_time":1701301216,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701410416","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Sustainable-Real-Estate-Investing-Building-a-Greener-and-More-Profitable-Future"},"id":254,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Sustainable-Real-Estate-Investing-Building-a-Greener-and-More-Profitable-Future","image":"banner_1701200257_21.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701200257_21.jpg","banner_title":"Sustainable Real Estate Investing","title":"Sustainable Real Estate Investing: Building a Greener and More Profitable Future","description":"<p>With the globe facing more urgent environmental problems, sustainability has become a crucial consideration when investing in real estate. Sustainable real estate investing entails purchasing homes that are energy-efficient, environmentally friendly, and compliant with morally and responsibly minded behaviour, rather than just focusing on financial gain. This article discusses sustainable real estate investing, highlighting its benefits and significance for investors.<br />\nEnvironmental Responsibility: Ecologically friendly methods are given top priority in sustainable real estate investing. This comprises eco-friendly materials, low-impact architectural designs, and energy-efficient structures. These characteristics lessen carbon footprints and promote a cleaner, more environmentally friendly world.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Financial Savings</strong></p>\n\n<p>Sustainable features frequently result in large financial savings. Green technologies can prolong the lifespan of a property&#39;s components, lowering maintenance and repair expenses, while energy-efficient structures have lower power bills.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Drawing in Modern Tenants</strong></p>\n\n<p>Renters nowadays are becoming more environmentally sensitive, particularly millennials and Generation Z. Properties that are sustainable have an advantage over other properties in the market because they draw renters who care about the environment and are prepared to pay more for a cleaner place to live or work.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Resilience to Regulatory Changes</strong></p>\n\n<p>Sustainable homes are more likely to adhere to the increasingly stringent environmental rules enforced by governments across the globe, hence mitigating the danger of expensive retrofits and fines.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Long-Term Investment Value</strong></p>\n\n<p>As sustainable properties become increasingly in demand, their value tends to increase. They appeal to long-term investors because they provide stability against market swings and economic risks.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Wide Range of Investment Opportunities</strong></p>\n\n<p>Sustainable real estate includes residential, commercial, and industrial buildings. Because of this variety, investors can select the kind of real estate that best fits their objectives for sustainability.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Impact on Society and Ethics</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investing in sustainable real estate involves more than just the numbers. It enables investors to positively influence society and help create a more responsible and sustainable future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong><br />\nSustainable real estate investing is a forward-thinking strategy that balances ethical and environmental responsibility with financial success. Investors that prioritise sustainability stand to win financially as well as contribute to a future that is more robust and sustainable. By highlighting the advantages and significance of sustainable real estate investing, this article hopes to inspire readers to learn more about this expanding market and incorporate morally and environmentally sound decisions into their real estate holdings. By doing this, investors can benefit from a more prosperous and environmentally friendly future for themselves and future generations.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-Bhavya Shah</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Sustainable Real Estate Investing: Building a Greener and More Profitable Future","seo_description":"Sustainable real estate investing is a fundamental change in the way we think about investing in real estate, not merely a fad. This piece explores the expanding field of sustainable real estate and explains why it's critical for investors who want to have a portfolio of properties that is both profitable and environmentally responsible. It looks at the advantages, tactics, and moral implications of sustainable real estate investing.","seo_keywords":"Sustainability, Investment, Real Estate, Shivalik","seo_image":"banner_1701200328_2.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701200328_2.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Sustainability","tag_lower":"sustainability"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"}],"tags_array":["Sustainability","Investment","Real Estate","Shivalik"],"tags_commaseparted":"Sustainability,Investment,Real Estate,Shivalik","published_time":1701196200,"published_date":"29 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1701200257,"date_format":"","date_time":"01:07 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"29 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"01:07 AM"},"updated_at":"Nov 29, 2023","updated_at_time":1701236634,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701236643","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Real-Estate-Investments-Choosing-Between-Residential-and-Commercial-Properties"},"id":253,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Real-Estate-Investments-Choosing-Between-Residential-and-Commercial-Properties","image":"banner_1701118712_34.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701118712_34.jpg","banner_title":"Real Estate Investments: Choosing Between Residential and Commercial Properties","title":"Real Estate Investments: Choosing Between Residential and Commercial Properties","description":"<p>Real estate investment has always been one of the most preferred investments, yielding long-term benefits and providing a lucrative way to grow one&#39;s wealth. Beyond property ownership, an investor benefits from passive income in the form of rent, tax savings, relatively low volatility, capital appreciation, and portfolio diversification. Often, an investment requires thorough research and insights to make an informed and rational decision. In the case of real estate, with a wide variety of possibilities and market dynamics, it is important to consider which investment suits best, given all the internal and external socio-economic factors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>One may be a seasoned investor or a newcomer in the world of real estate, but the question of whether to invest in residential or commercial properties is always daunting for investors. Each type of property offers its own unique features and benefits that can offer a substantial return on investment.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Traditionally, owning a house is every individual&#39;s dream in their lifetime, making residential real estate a popular choice of investment. The cultural significance of owning a home also symbolizes financial stability and success. India&#39;s housing market has been consistently growing with the rise in urbanization and more people moving to cities. Sustained income and residential property investment are synonymous, as the perpetual need for shelter ensures a steady stream of rental income and consistent demand. The recent evolution and surge in average home rentals solidify residential properties as a promising avenue for investment. Additionally, residential properties are relatively less complex to navigate, making them more accessible for beginner investors and first-time buyers. Investment in residential properties always has twofold benefits for investors, as it serves the purpose of personal use alongside financial gain. Despite the multitude of factors, the real estate space has withstood the test of time and proven to be an ideal investment for medium and low-risk appetite investors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>On the other hand, commercial properties have their own unique benefits with a close association with trade and economic growth. As cities grow, the need for trade, commerce, and businesses also grows. Commercial properties range from office and retail spaces to warehouses and industrial houses, creating the potential for investors to invest in niche markets and capitalize on specific market trends. While residential properties benefit from steady rental income, commercial properties benefit from higher rental yields, as businesses are willing to pay premium rents for prime locations. Moreover, commercial property investors enjoy stability for an extended period of time, with multi-year leases ensuring uninterrupted income. In the majority of commercial properties, the onus of maintenance falls on the tenant, reducing the financial responsibility of the owner. Commercial real estate has also demonstrated resilience amidst the global economic turmoil and is gradually picking up pace due to an ever-growing workforce and the need to accommodate decentralized growth corridors.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The choice between investing in residential or commercial property depends on an individual&#39;s goals and circumstances. An investor looking for a steady and predictable income with a more straightforward management experience may find it suitable to invest in residential properties. However, with a slightly higher risk appetite, the capability to bear upfront costs, and the ability to handle complex management, commercial properties could be the way to go.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">- Sharvari Parikh</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Real Estate Investments: Choosing Between Residential and Commercial Properties","seo_description":"Real estate investment offers long-term benefits like passive income, rent, tax savings, low volatility, capital appreciation, and portfolio diversification. Residential properties are popular for beginners and low-risk investors, while commercial properties offer higher rental yields, longer leases, and tenant maintenance. The choice between residential and commercial properties depends on individual goals and circumstances.","seo_keywords":"Real Estate, Investment, Commercial, Residential, Shivalik, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1701118776_93.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1701118776_93.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Commercial","tag_lower":"commercial"},{"text":"Residential","tag_lower":"residential"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Investment","Commercial","Residential","Shivalik","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Investment,Commercial,Residential,Shivalik,Ahmedabad","published_time":1701023400,"published_date":"27 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1701118712,"date_format":"","date_time":"02:28 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"28 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"02:28 AM"},"updated_at":"Nov 28, 2023","updated_at_time":1701171067,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701171100","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Greenview-Sample-House-Launched-at-Adani-Shantigram"},"id":252,"project_id":"35","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Greenview-Sample-House-Launched-at-Adani-Shantigram","image":"banner_1700918023_64.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700918023_64.jpg","banner_title":"Greenview Sample House Launched at Adani Shantigram","title":"Greenview Sample House Launched at Adani Shantigram","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>With the recent sample house launch of Shivalik Greenview at Adani Shantigram, you can elevate your lifestyle. Every detail of Greenview is carefully crafted to redefine your standard of living, making it more than just a residence.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Located within the lush surroundings of Adani Shantigram, Greenview redefines the concept of modern living.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Luxury Living Redefined</strong></p>\n\n<p>The sample house at Shivalik Greenview is more than just a showcase; it reflects luxury and comfort. The minute you step inside, you&#39;ll be immersed in a world where every corner is carefully designed to make your home feel alive. The 3 BHK + work-from-home luxury apartments and penthouses are elegantly designed, offering a seamless blend of aesthetics and functionality.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Smart Spaces for Modern Living</strong></p>\n\n<p>With modern lifestyles where working from home has become the norm, Shivalik Greenview understands the importance of creating smart spaces. The apartments are not just homes; they are functional spaces where the boundaries between work and life seamlessly blend. You can create a tranquil and professional work environment in your home office, with plenty of natural light.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Prime Location of Adani Shantigram</strong></p>\n\n<p>A prime location like Shantigram cannot be ignored &ndash; a prime location that adds to the appeal of Shivalik Greenview. Conveniently situated in Ahmedabad, this residential project provides more than just a home; it offers a lifestyle. The green surroundings complemented by the modern infrastructure create an environment that is both refreshing and relaxing.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Peaceful Living in Your Home</strong></p>\n\n<p>Enjoy the comforts of home while escaping the chaos of the city. Shivalik Greenview promises peaceful living in your own home. The house embodies a thoughtful design that embraces serenity, making it a peaceful haven within the city. Whether you&#39;re enjoying a quiet evening on your balcony or relaxing in the spacious living area, every moment at Shivalik Greenview is designed for tranquility.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>First Pre-Certified Platinum Rated Green Building</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investing in a home at Shivalik Greenview means investing in sustainability. The project proudly holds the distinction of being the FIRST PRE-CERTIFIED PLATINUM RATED GREEN BUILDING. This not only reflects a commitment to eco-friendly living but also ensures that your home is a responsible and energy-efficient home.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Elevate Your Lifestyle with Greenview</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Greenview&#39;s recent sample house launch at Adani Shantigram is not just a glimpse into the future of real estate; it&#39;s an invitation to elevate your lifestyle. Invest in a lifestyle that combines modernity with nature, and sophistication with simplicity.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Experience the future of luxury living with Shivalik Greenview.</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><strong><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-</span><span style=\"color:#dddddd;\">Kishan Thakkar</span></strong></h5>\n","seo_title":"Greenview Sample House Launched at Adani Shantigram","seo_description":"Shivalik Group launches Greenview at Adani Shantigram, a luxurious sample house with modern amenities. Live a luxurious lifestyle with the latest in design and comfort.","seo_keywords":"Sample House Ready, Shivalik, Greenview, Shantigram, Home, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1700918105_58.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700918105_58.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Sample House","tag_lower":"sample house"},{"text":"Greenview","tag_lower":"greenview"},{"text":"Shantigram","tag_lower":"shantigram"},{"text":"Homes","tag_lower":"homes"},{"text":"3BHK","tag_lower":"3bhk"},{"text":"Apartments","tag_lower":"apartments"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Sample House","Greenview","Shantigram","Homes","3BHK","Apartments","Shivalik","Real Estate","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Sample House,Greenview,Shantigram,Homes,3BHK,Apartments,Shivalik,Real Estate,Ahmedabad","published_time":1700850600,"published_date":"25 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700918023,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:43 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"25 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"06:43 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 27, 2023","updated_at_time":1701069533,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701069545","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Building-Homes-Enhancing-Lives--A-Well-Being-Perspective"},"id":250,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Building-Homes-Enhancing-Lives--A-Well-Being-Perspective","image":"banner_1700840307_17.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700840307_17.jpg","banner_title":"Building Homes, Enhancing Lives - A Well-Being Perspective","title":"Building Homes, Enhancing Lives - A Well-Being Perspective.","description":"<p>One of the core principles that sets Shivalik apart from others is its unwavering commitment to enhancing the overall well-being of its customers. It is a guiding philosophy that resonates with every aspect of Shivalik&#39;s projects. The company understands that a home is not just a physical structure but a place where people live, create memories and strive for a better quality of life. As a result, Shivalik goes above and beyond to develop amenities in its buildings that contribute to the health, happiness, and overall satisfaction of its residents.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik&#39;s commitment to the well-being of its customers is evident in the fitness and recreational amenities it provides. Most of Shivalik&#39;s properties are equipped with state-of-the-art fitness centers. These amenities promote physical health and an active lifestyle. Regular exercise is essential for maintaining good health, and having a gym or sports facilities within the building encourages residents to make fitness a part of their daily routine. This not only saves time but also creates a convenient and motivating environment for residents to prioritize their health.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Additionally, Shivalik understands the importance of green spaces and nature in promoting well-being. Many of their properties feature lush gardens, landscaped open areas, and even rooftop gardens. The presence of greenery in and around a living space has been scientifically proven to reduce stress, improve air quality, and enhance overall mental well-being. Residents can enjoy peaceful walks, practice yoga, or simply unwind amidst the serenity of these green spaces. Shivalik&#39;s commitment to nature extends to sustainable and eco-friendly building practices, contributing to a healthier environment for both residents and the larger community.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Mental wellness is a critical aspect of overall well-being, and Shivalik takes this seriously. The company often includes meditation and wellness centers in its properties. They provide a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life, allowing residents to find inner peace and balance in the midst of urban living.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik also promotes social interaction and a sense of community among its residents. Many of their properties feature community halls, and recreation rooms where residents can come together, share experiences, and build lasting friendships. This social aspect is often overlooked but plays a vital role in overall well-being. Strong social connections are linked to increased happiness and a sense of belonging, and Shivalik&#39;s amenities facilitate these connections by providing spaces for residents to engage with one another.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>By providing amenities that promote physical health, mental wellness, social interaction, and safety, Shivalik goes beyond the ordinary in creating living spaces that enrich the lives of its residents. The company&#39;s commitment to well-being sets a new standard in the real estate industry, and it is a testament to their dedication to enhancing the lives of those who choose to call Shivalik properties their home.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">- Hardi Shah</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Building Homes, Enhancing Lives - A Well-Being Perspective.","seo_description":"Shivalik, a prominent real estate company, prioritizes customer well-being through modern fitness centers, lush gardens, and eco-friendly building practices. The company also emphasizes green spaces, such as rooftop gardens and meditation centers, to reduce stress and improve air quality. This commitment sets a new standard in the industry.","seo_keywords":"Home, Real Estate, Lifestyle, Shivalik, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1700840404_39.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700840404_39.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Lifestyle","tag_lower":"lifestyle"},{"text":"Home","tag_lower":"home"},{"text":"#Shivalik","tag_lower":"#shivalik"},{"text":"#Real Estate","tag_lower":"#real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Lifestyle","Home","#Shivalik","#Real Estate","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Lifestyle,Home,#Shivalik,#Real Estate,Ahmedabad","published_time":1700764200,"published_date":"24 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700840307,"date_format":"","date_time":"09:08 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"24 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"09:08 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 24, 2023","updated_at_time":1700840404,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1700891535","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/redevelopment-of-a-real-estate-project-in-gujarat"},"id":249,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"12","slug":"redevelopment-of-a-real-estate-project-in-gujarat","image":"banner_1700824901_41.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700824901_41.jpg","banner_title":"Redevelopment of a Real Estate Project in Gujarat","title":"Redevelopment of a Real Estate Project in Gujarat","description":"<p><input alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.reecosys.com/api/uploads/blog/2023/11/1700822330_unnamed_(4).png\" style=\"width: 213px; height: 186px;\" type=\"image\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Author - <strong>CA Harsh Mehta</strong></p>\n\n<p>Mobile Number :&nbsp;9998059270</p>\n\n<p>Email Id :&nbsp;harsh@gujreraexperts.com</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Redevelopment of real estate projects has become a vital aspect of urban development, especially in densely populated areas where land is scarce. In a dynamic landscape like Gujarat, where urbanization is rapidly advancing, the process of redevelopment holds immense potential to transform outdated structures into modern, sustainable, and aesthetically appealing developments.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Redevelopment is the process of demolishing and reconstructing an existing building or a group of buildings to create new and improved structures that meet the current needs and standards of the occupants and the society.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This article aims to provide a comprehensive insight into the process, benefits, and legal guidelines surrounding real estate redevelopment in Gujarat which is governed by the Gujarat Ownership Flats Act, 1973 and its amendment in 2019. We will also briefly include snapshots of important judgements on redevelopment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Reasons of Redevelopment.</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>To replace old and dilapidated buildings that are unsafe and unhealthy to live in;</li>\n\t<li>To increase the floor space index (FSI) and utilize the land potential more efficiently;</li>\n\t<li>To provide larger and better amenities to the residents, such as parking, fire safety, security, etc.;</li>\n\t<li>To enhance the aesthetic and environmental quality of the area;</li>\n\t<li>To generate revenue from the sale of surplus units or commercial spaces.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><br />\n<strong>Redevelopment is done by:-</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The owners or members of the building or society themselves.</li>\n\t<li>The developers or builders who enter into an agreement with the owners or members.</li>\n\t<li>The public authorities, such as Gujarat Housing Board (GHB), Urban Local Bodies (ULBs), Urban Development Authorities (UDAs), etc.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Legal guidelines for redevelopment in Gujarat.</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done with the consent of not less than seventy-five per cent of the members of the society.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done after twenty-five years of the issuance of the permission for development or if the building is declared dilapidated, ruinous or dangerous by the concerned authority.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done by a registered developer or builder who has experience in redevelopment projects.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done as per the Common GDCR, Redevelopment Rules, Affordable Housing Policy, etc.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done with all the necessary clearances and permissions from various authorities, such as GHB, ULBs, UDAs, RERA, fire department, environment department, etc.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done with safety norms and environmental standards.</li>\n\t<li>The redevelopment has to be done with transparency and accountability.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Process of Redevelopment</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Initiation:</strong> The redevelopment can be initiated by the managing committee of the society suo-moto or by an application from at least one-fourth of the members of the flats. The managing committee has to call for a special general meeting within a period of one month on receipt of the application. The meeting has to follow the rules and bylaws of the society with respect to convening, notice, agenda, quorum, decision, agreement, minutes, etc.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Consent: </strong>The consent of not less than seventy-five per cent of the total members of the society for redevelopment is necessary. The consent has to be obtained in writing.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Developer selection:</strong> The managing committee along with the society members has to select a developer for construction of the project. The proposals of redevelopment received from various developers shall be evaluated based on various parameters, such as financial capability, technical expertise, quality standards, track record, etc. However, the society shall give more priority to the experience and project completion capacity of the builder over other things. The selection can be from the internal references or through a tender bidding process.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Registered Development Agreement: </strong>The society has to select the best developer or builder and enter into a registered development agreement with him. The society can engage advocate/consultant for preparation/verification of the documents so as to safeguard their rights. The agreement has to specify the roles and responsibilities of each party, the scope and specifications of work, the payment terms and schedule, the penalty clauses for delay or default, the dispute resolution mechanism, etc. The said development agreement must be registered with the sub-registrar. Currently the stamp duty of 3.5% of the Jantri Value and registration fees of 1% of Jantri value is payable on the same.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Plan Approval and Permissions:</strong> The developer or builder has to obtain all the necessary clearances and permissions from various authorities, such as GHB, ULBs, UDAs, RERA, fire department, environment department, etc. for carrying out the redevelopment project. The developer or builder has to comply with all the applicable rules and regulations, such as Common GDCR (General Development Control Regulations), Redevelopment Rules, Affordable Housing Policy, etc.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Demolition:</strong> The developer or builder has to demolish the existing building or society after vacating all the members and providing them with alternative accommodation and rent as agreed upon. The demolition has to be done in a safe and scientific manner without causing any damage or inconvenience to the neighboring properties or people.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Construction:</strong> The developer or builder has to construct the new building or society as per the approved layout plan and design within the stipulated time frame. The construction has to be done with quality materials and workmanship under the supervision of the architect or project management consultant. The construction has to follow all the safety norms and environmental standards.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Handover: </strong>The developer or builder has to hand over the possession of the new flats or units to the members after obtaining all the completion certificates and occupancy certificates from the concerned authorities. The developer or builder has to also hand over all the documents and records related to the redevelopment project to the managing committee.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Benefits of Redevelopment</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Infrastructure Upgrade:</strong> Redevelopment projects provide an opportunity to upgrade and modernize infrastructure, including roads, drainage systems, and utilities, enhancing overall living conditions.</h3>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Increased Housing Stock:</strong> Redevelopment optimizes land use by replacing old structures with modern, multi-story buildings, thereby increasing the available housing stock.</h3>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Enhanced Aesthetics:</strong> The introduction of contemporary architectural designs and landscaping improves the visual appeal of the area, contributing to the overall urban aesthetics.</h3>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Improved Amenities:</strong> Redevelopment projects often incorporate amenities such as green spaces, recreational facilities, and commercial spaces, enhancing the quality of life for residents.</h3>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<h3><strong>Economic Growth:</strong> The real estate and construction industries experience growth through increased demand for skilled labor, building materials, and related services, fostering economic development.</h3>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Some important Judgements in relation to Redevelopment</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Hansaben Ratubhai Prajapati v. State of Gujarat. &nbsp;</strong><br />\n(Gujarat High Court decided on 11-04-2023)</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWhen a redevelopment scheme is in the interest of public at large, the entire project cannot be put to a standstill at the behest of few persons (14 petitioners) when 75% of the occupants have consented to the redevelopment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Adityaraj Builders v. State of Maharashtra.</strong><br />\n(Bombay High Court decided on 17-02-2023.)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>A development agreement (DA) between a cooperative housing society and a developer for developing society&rsquo;s property (land, building, apartments, flats, garages, godowns, galas) requires to be stamped.</li>\n\t<li>The development agreement need not be signed by individual members of society as a mandate. Even if individual members do not sign the DA, it controls the re-development and society members&rsquo; rights.</li>\n\t<li>A Permanent Alternate Accommodation Agreements (PAAA) between developer and an individual society member does not require to be signed on behalf of the society.</li>\n\t<li>Stamp cannot be levied twice. Once the DA is stamped, the PAAA cannot be separately assessed to stamp beyond the requirement of Rs. 100 under Section 4(1), if it specifically relates to rebuilt or reconstructed premises in lieu of the old premises used/occupied by the member. The same applies even if the PAAA includes an additional area available to the member, since it is not a purchase or a transfer but is in lieu of the member&rsquo;s old premises. The stamp on DA includes reconstruction of every unit in the society building.</li>\n\t<li>If PAAA is limited to rebuilt premises in the absence of actual purchase for consideration of any additional area, such PAAA is an incidental document under Section 4(1) of the Stamp Act.</li>\n\t<li>PAAA between a developer and a society member must be additionally stamped if it provides for purchase for actual stated consideration and a purchase price of additional area beyond the area given to the member against the earlier premises.</li>\n\t<li>Assessing stamp on PAAA on construction cost of the new premises in lieu of old premises cannot be sustained.</li>\n\t<li>Reference to redevelopment and homes includes garages, galas, commercial and industrial use and every form of redevelopment of the society.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Redevelopment is a complex and challenging process that requires careful planning and execution. It involves various stakeholders, such as members, managing committee, developer, builder, architect, consultant, authorities, etc. It also involves various risks, such as legal disputes, financial losses, delays, defects, etc. Therefore, it is advisable to seek professional guidance and assistance from experts in the field of redevelopment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Redevelopment is a powerful tool for revitalizing urban spaces in Gujarat, catering to the growing demands of modern living while simultaneously enhancing the aesthetic and economic aspects of the region. By adhering to the established legal guidelines and fostering cooperation between stakeholders, successful redevelopment projects can contribute significantly to the state&#39;s urban development narrative. As Gujarat progresses towards a more vibrant urban future, redevelopment stands as a testament to innovation, sustainable growth, and community development.</p>\n","seo_title":"Redevelopment of a Real Estate Project in Gujarat","seo_description":"Redevelopment of real estate projects has become a vital aspect of urban development, especially in densely populated areas where land is scarce. In a dynamic landscape like Gujarat, where urbanization is rapidly advancing, the process of redevelopment holds immense potential to transform outdated structures into modern, sustainable, and aesthetically appealing developments.","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"banner_1700827140_7.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700827140_7.jpg","tags_array":"","tags_commaseparted":"","published_time":1700677800,"published_date":"23 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700808059,"date_format":"","date_time":"12:10 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"24 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"12:10 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 27, 2023","updated_at_time":1701086727,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701067186","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Make-your-4-BHK-flat-more-spacious"},"id":248,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"8","slug":"Make-your-4-BHK-flat-more-spacious","image":"banner_1700748623_68.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700748623_68.jpg","banner_title":"Make your 4 BHK apartment more spacious","title":"Make your 4 BHK apartment more spacious","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>Picture this: after a long day at work, you return to a beautifully designed, well-lit living room. You sink into your plush sofa, taking in the spaciousness, the clutter-free surfaces, and the clever storage solutions that have turned your once-cramped flat into a serene retreat.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Gone are the days of feeling suffocated by clutter or navigating around oversized furniture. With these fantastic ideas, your 4 BHK flat will soon feel expansive, organized, and simply magnificent.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Leverage the Magic of Mirrors</strong></p>\n\n<p>Mirrors create an illusion of more space by reflecting light and providing depth. Strategically place mirrors on walls, shelves, or as part of your furniture, such as a mirrored coffee table or dresser.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Illuminate Wisely</strong></p>\n\n<p>Adequate lighting can make a difference in making your 4 BHK residential flat feel open and inviting. Let the natural light flood in by keeping drapes and blinds open during the day. Use ceiling, floor, and table lamps to create a warm and welcoming atmosphere.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Choose Furniture Thoughtfully</strong></p>\n\n<p>Opt for furniture that maximizes space. Avoid bulky pieces and instead select multi-functional and space-saving options. A storage ottoman can double as both a footrest and a place to stow blankets and pillows, while a sofa bed can provide extra sleeping space for guests.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Embrace Lighter Colors</strong></p>\n\n<p>The choice of colors for your walls and furnishings can significantly impact the perception of space. Lighter shades like white, cream, and beige create an illusion of a larger, more open area, while darker colors can make a room feel confined. Opt for brighter colors on your walls, curtains, and furniture upholstery.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Keep Surfaces Clutter-Free</strong></p>\n\n<p>One of the easiest ways to make your 4 BHK residential flat in Ahmedabad feel more spacious is by maintaining clutter-free surfaces. Instead of crowding tables and shelves with numerous decorative items, choose a few carefully selected pieces that enhance the overall ambiance.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Define Zones</strong></p>\n\n<p>Create distinct zones within your four-bedroom flat using rugs, furniture placement, and lighting. Whether it&#39;s a reading nook, dining area, or workspace, these defined areas can help you make the most of your space and foster a sense of coziness.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Utilize Vertical Space</strong></p>\n\n<p>Maximizing vertical space becomes crucial when floor space is limited. Install shelves, bookcases, and wall-mounted storage to organize your belongings and free up valuable floor space.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Innovative Storage Solutions</strong></p>\n\n<p>Get creative with storage options such as built-in shelving, under-bed storage, and storage ottomans. These unique solutions will help you make the most of your space and keep it clutter-free.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Bonus Idea by Lofy:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Consider investing in furniture with dual functions to maximize space efficiently. A sofa bed serves as both a comfortable seating area during the day and a cozy bed for guests at night, while a storage ottoman can provide a place to relax and store blankets, pillows, and more.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-&nbsp;Jayshree Ochwani</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Make your 4 BHK flat more spacious","seo_description":"To create a serene retreat in a 4 BHK flat, use mirrors, adequate lighting, furniture that maximizes space, and clutter-free surfaces. Define zones with rugs, furniture placement, and lighting. Maximize vertical space with shelves, bookcases, and wall-mounted storage. Invest in dual-functional furniture for efficient space utilization.","seo_keywords":"Interior, Home, Real Estate, Lofy, Ahmedabad,","seo_image":"banner_1700748751_60.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700748751_60.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Interior","tag_lower":"interior"},{"text":"4BHK","tag_lower":"4bhk"},{"text":"Spacious","tag_lower":"spacious"},{"text":"Home","tag_lower":"home"},{"text":"Lofy","tag_lower":"lofy"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"}],"tags_array":["Interior","4BHK","Spacious","Home","Lofy","Ahmedabad","Real Estate"],"tags_commaseparted":"Interior,4BHK,Spacious,Home,Lofy,Ahmedabad,Real Estate","published_time":1700677800,"published_date":"23 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700748623,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:40 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"23 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"07:40 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 24, 2023","updated_at_time":1700824297,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1700824341","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Buying-vs-Renting-Real-Estate"},"id":246,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Buying-vs-Renting-Real-Estate","image":"banner_1701682219_37.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1701682219_37.jpeg","banner_title":"Buying vs. Renting Real Estate","title":"Buying vs. Renting Real Estate","description":"<p>A major dream of any individual&rsquo;s life is owning a home. However, deciding whether to buy or rent is a big choice that impacts your aspirations, lifestyle, and financial stability. Whichever choice you select, it will all depend on your financial and lifestyle circumstances. Both may need some work to maintain and a consistent source of income (so you can pay the bills and related expenses).</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The decision to buy a house or rent one can depend on a variety of factors, such as your financial situation, lifestyle, and future plans. In general, buying a house can be a good investment in the long run, as property values tend to appreciate over time.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Buying a property comes with the advantages of building your own equity and passing it over to the next generations as an asset. This pattern has been in practice for a very long period of time and has been proven to be a profitable move. Investing in a property not only means putting your foot down practically and financially but it also brings along a sense of community building, stability, and security to your near and dear ones. In your own space, you are at will to remodel/ re-shape according to your personal needs without any hassle of permissions and dependency on the landlord in the case of rented properties.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Renting on the other hand is preferred by people who are always on their toes and might require to relocate every now and then. Renting is considered as a temporary housing option as it does not build any long-term equity or asset. However, these rented properties prove to be an additional source of income for the owner. Rented properties do not provide tax-saving benefits which in turn is a loss to the occupant. The market trends for renting have no specifics or insights to study which gives the owner the power to manipulate the occupant for a higher rent. There is also a significant risk of sudden eviction to the occupant as the landlord might always look for higher rental income irrespective of the occupant&rsquo;s conditions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nShivalik Group also encourages the general public to opt for buying instead of renting real estate property by promoting customer-friendly payment schemes wherein the buyer can easily analyse the difference between EMI cost and rental cost and is easier on the customer&rsquo;s pocket.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Dhruv Jain</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Buying vs. Renting Real Estate","seo_description":"Owning a home is a dream, but the decision depends on personal financial circumstances and future plans. Buying offers advantages like building equity, while renting provides temporary housing without long-term benefits. Shivalik Group promotes buying over renting.","seo_keywords":"Buying, Renting, Real Estate, Shivalik, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1700662128_21.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700662128_21.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Buying","tag_lower":"buying"},{"text":"Renting","tag_lower":"renting"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Buying","Renting","Shivalik","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Buying,Renting,Shivalik,Ahmedabad","published_time":1700591400,"published_date":"22 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700662033,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:37 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"22 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"07:37 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 04, 2023","updated_at_time":1701682582,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1701682600","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/Guide-to-real-estate-NRI-investment"},"id":245,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"Guide-to-real-estate-NRI-investment","image":"banner_1700568921_78.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700568921_78.jpg","banner_title":"Guide to real estate NRI investment","title":"Guide to real estate NRI investment","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>Real estate is one of the most preferred asset classes for NRIs who want to invest in India. The Indian real estate sector has shown resilience and growth in the past few years, despite the global economic slowdown and the COVID-19 pandemic. According to a report by 360 Realtors, NRIs invested $13.1 billion in the Indian real estate market in FY21 and the inflow is likely to grow 12% to reach $14.9 billion in FY22 &amp; FY23.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>There are many factors that make real estate investment attractive for NRIs, such as</strong></p>\n\n<p>Favorable currency exchange rate: The depreciation of the Indian rupee against major foreign currencies like the US dollar, the Euro, and the Singapore dollar gives NRIs a higher purchasing power and a better return on investment.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Demand for luxury homes</strong></p>\n\n<p>NRIs often look for spacious and comfortable homes that suit their lifestyle and offer amenities like security, clubhouse, gym, pool, etc. The demand for luxury homes in India has increased in recent years, especially in cities like Ahmedabad, Gandhinagar, Mumbai, Bengaluru, Delhi-NCR, Hyderabad, and Chennai. These cities also offer high rental yields and capital appreciation for luxury properties.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Ease of buying process</strong></p>\n\n<p>The government has simplified the rules and regulations for NRI investment in real estate in India. NRIs do not need any prior permission from the Reserve Bank of India (RBI) or any other authority to buy residential or commercial properties in India. They can also avail of home loans from Indian banks and financial institutions at attractive interest rates.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Emotional and sentimental value</strong></p>\n\n<p>Many NRIs have an emotional attachment to their homeland and want to own property in their native place. Buying a home in India also gives them a sense of security and belongingness. They can also use their property as a vacation home or a retirement home when they visit India or settle down here.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>However, before investing in real estate in India, NRIs should also be aware of some challenges and risks, such as</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Tax implications</strong></p>\n\n<p>NRIs have to pay taxes on their income from real estate in India, such as rental income, capital gains, and wealth tax. They also have to comply with the tax laws of their country of residence and avoid double taxation by claiming tax benefits under the Double Taxation Avoidance Agreement (DTAA) between India and their country.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Legal issues</strong></p>\n\n<p>NRIs should verify the legal status and ownership of the property they are buying and ensure that it has all the necessary approvals and clearances from the authorities.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Maintenance and management</strong></p>\n\n<p>NRIs should also consider how they will maintain and manage their property in India when they are not physically present here. They should appoint a reliable caretaker or a property management company to look after their property, collect rent, pay bills, handle repairs, etc. They should also keep themselves updated with the market trends and the value of their property.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Why choose Shivalik Group for your real estate investment?</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>If you are an NRI looking for a trusted and reputed real estate developer in India, you should choose Shivalik Group. Shivalik Group is one of the leading real estate developers in Gujarat, India with over 25 years of experience and expertise in building quality homes and commercial spaces. Shivalik Group offers you many benefits, such as trust and legacy, quality and design, prime location, and customer support.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>So, if you are an NRI looking for a smart and profitable real estate investment in India, you should choose Shivalik Group as your partner. Shivalik Group will help you find your dream home or your ideal commercial space in Gujarat and make your investment journey smooth and hassle-free. To know more about Shivalik Group and its projects, visit https://www.shivalikgroup.com/ or call +91-079-4020-0000.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Piyush Golani</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Guide to real estate NRI investment | Shivalik Group","seo_description":"Learn why real estate is a lucrative asset class for NRIs who want to invest in India and how Shivalik Group can help you find the best property in Gujarat.","seo_keywords":"NRI, Investment, Real Estate, Shivalik, Ahmedabad, India","seo_image":"banner_1700568992_31.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700568992_31.jpg","tags":[{"text":"NRI","tag_lower":"nri"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"}],"tags_array":["NRI","Investment","Real Estate","Shivalik","Ahmedabad","India"],"tags_commaseparted":"NRI,Investment,Real Estate,Shivalik,Ahmedabad,India","published_time":1700591400,"published_date":"22 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700568921,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:45 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"21 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"05:45 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 21, 2023","updated_at_time":1700568992,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1700569957","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/shivalik:-area-upgradation--from-ordinary-to-prime"},"id":242,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"shivalik:-area-upgradation--from-ordinary-to-prime","image":"banner_1700316491_1.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1700316491_1.jpg","banner_title":"Shivalik: Area Upgradation - From Ordinary to Prime","title":"Shivalik: Area Upgradation - From Ordinary to Prime","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>Over the years, Shivalik has demonstrated a remarkable commitment to transforming ordinary areas into prime locations. The company&#39;s journey in the real estate industry has been marked by a series of projects that have not only reshaped Ahmedabad&#39;s urban landscape but have also elevated the living standards of its residents. Through a strategic and thoughtful approach, Shivalik has managed to turn lesser-known neighborhoods into sought-after destinations.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nLet&#39;s take a closer look at some of Shivalik&#39;s key projects that exemplify its dedication to area upgradation and development.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Villa: A Landmark Bungalow Project on Rajpath Road</p>\n\n<p>The carefully designed and meticulously executed Shivalik Villa not only provided a comfortable living environment but also set the stage for the company&#39;s future endeavors. It showcased Shivalik&#39;s commitment to quality, aesthetics, and functionality, which would become hallmarks of their projects.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nSachin Tower: Redefining Shyamal</p>\n\n<p>The iconic Sachin Tower on Shyamal Road not only redefined the skyline of Shyamal but also became a landmark in Ahmedabad. Sachin Tower brought a new level of modernity to the neighborhood, making it a prime residential and commercial hub. Its success demonstrated Shivalik&#39;s ability to create developments.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Business Center: A Business Hub in Ambli</p>\n\n<p>Continuing its mission of area upgradation, Shivalik Business Center near Ambli emerged as a significant commercial hub. This project not only provided office spaces but also contributed to the economic growth of the region. Shivalik recognized the need for well-planned and strategically located business centers, and the success of this endeavor underlined the company&#39;s commitment to enhancing every aspect of urban life.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Park View 1 &amp; 2: Shaping the Future of Shela</p>\n\n<p>Shela, once a relatively unknown area, transformed with Shivalik&#39;s visionary project, Park View. The success of Shivalik Park View 1 was a testament to Shivalik&#39;s ability to anticipate the changing demands of the urban population. This residential project introduced a modern and sustainable way of living, complete with state-of-the-art amenities and green spaces. The overwhelming response from homebuyers highlighted the growing demand for such developments in the Shela, and it was clear that Shivalik was at the forefront of area upgradation and development.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nFollowing the success of Shivalik Park View 1, Shivalik introduced Park View 2, further cementing its reputation as a developer committed to enhancing the quality of life in the regions it touches.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><br />\n<br />\nShivalik&rsquo;s projects have not only transformed ordinary neighborhoods into prime locations but have also enriched the lives of the people who call these places home. Shivalik&#39;s approach is not merely about constructing buildings but about shaping the future of communities and urban landscapes. Shivalik&#39;s commitment to excellence, innovation, and the well-being of its customers continues to shine through in every project it undertakes.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">- Hardi Shah</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Shivalik: Area Upgradation - From Ordinary to Prime","seo_description":"When it comes to real estate in Ahmedabad, Shivalik is a trendsetter that turns drab neighbourhoods into tourist hotspots. Examples of its dedication to improving the neighbourhood include the Shivalik Villa and Sachin Tower residential complexes and the Shivalik Business Centre and Park View residential developments. Shivalik's strategic strategy, commitment to quality, and community enrichment define its effective path in developing thriving urban landscapes.","seo_keywords":"Shivalik, Ahmedabad, Upgrade, Real Estate","seo_image":"banner_1700316594_19.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1700316594_19.jpg","tags":[{"text":"#Real Estate","tag_lower":"#real estate"},{"text":"#Shivalik","tag_lower":"#shivalik"},{"text":"#Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"#ahmedabad"},{"text":"#Upgrade","tag_lower":"#upgrade"}],"tags_array":["#Real Estate","#Shivalik","#Ahmedabad","#Upgrade"],"tags_commaseparted":"#Real Estate,#Shivalik,#Ahmedabad,#Upgrade","published_time":1700245800,"published_date":"18 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1700316491,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:38 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"18 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"07:38 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 18, 2023","updated_at_time":1700316594,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1700461059","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/twisted-tower-in-gift-city:-india’s-first-and-tallest-twisted-tower"},"id":239,"project_id":"175","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"twisted-tower-in-gift-city:-india’s-first-and-tallest-twisted-tower","image":"banner_1699546224_80.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1699546224_80.jpg","banner_title":"Twisted Tower in Gift City: India’s First and Tallest Twisted Tower","title":"Twisted Tower in Gift City: India’s First and Tallest Twisted Tower","description":"<p><strong>What is Twisted Tower in Gift City?</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\nTwisted Tower in Gift City is a stunning skyscraper that will be the one of tallest twisted tower in India. It is located in the heart of GIFT City, India&rsquo;s first operational smart city and international financial services center. The tower is named Shivalik Curv, and it is a project of Shivalik Group, one of the leading real estate developers in Gujarat.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Why is Twisted Tower in Gift City Unique?</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Twisted Tower in Gift City is unique because of its distinctive shape and design. The tower has a spiral twist that creates an illusion of movement and dynamism. The twist also enhances the structural stability and aerodynamics of the tower, making it more resistant to wind and seismic forces.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe tower is designed by a renowned architect who has created some of the most iconic buildings in India and abroad. The design is inspired by the curves of nature, such as the waves of the ocean, the petals of a flower, or the spiral of a shell.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>What are the Features and Benefits of Twisted Tower in Gift City?</strong></p>\n\n<p>The twisted Tower in Gift City will have 32&nbsp;floors and a height of 118&nbsp;meters, making it one of the tallest twisted towers in the world. The tower will offer premium office spaces for corporates, professionals, and entrepreneurs who want to work in a futuristic and vibrant environment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe tower will have state-of-the-art amenities and features, such as high-speed elevators, smart security systems, energy-efficient lighting, water harvesting, waste management, fire safety, and more. The tower will also have a sky lounge on the top floor, where the occupants can enjoy panoramic views of GIFT City and the surrounding landscape.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nTwisted Tower in Gift City will also be a green building that will follow the best practices of environmental sustainability. The tower will use renewable energy sources, such as solar panels and wind turbines, to reduce its carbon footprint and save on electricity costs. The tower will also use natural ventilation and cooling systems to reduce its dependence on air conditioning and heating systems.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>How to Own a Space in Twisted Tower in Gift City?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Twisted Tower in Gift City is not just a building, it is a vision. A vision to create a landmark that will showcase India&rsquo;s prowess in architecture and engineering. A vision to create a landmark that will attract global attention and admiration. A vision to create a landmark that will make every Indian proud.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Group invites you to be a part of this vision. To own a space in Twisted Tower in Gift City is to own a piece of history. To own a space in Twisted Tower in Gift City is to own a piece of art. To own a space in Twisted Tower in Gift City is to own a piece of the future.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nFor more details about Twisted Tower in Gift City, please visit our website or contact us today.</p>\n\n<h4><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">- Piyush Golani</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Twisted Tower in Gift City - India’s One of Tallest Twisted Tower","seo_description":"Shivalik Curv is a stunning skyscraper with a unique twisted shape in GIFT City. It offers premium office spaces with state-of-the-art amenities and features.","seo_keywords":"Curv, Twisted Tower, Landmark, Shivalik, GIFT City, Ahmedabad, Shivalik","seo_image":"banner_1699546315_85.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1699546315_85.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Twisted Tower","tag_lower":"twisted tower"},{"text":"Curv","tag_lower":"curv"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"},{"text":"Landmark","tag_lower":"landmark"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"}],"tags_array":["Twisted Tower","Curv","GIFT City","Landmark","Ahmedabad","Shivalik"],"tags_commaseparted":"Twisted Tower,Curv,GIFT City,Landmark,Ahmedabad,Shivalik","published_time":1699468200,"published_date":"09 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1699546224,"date_format":"","date_time":"09:40 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"09 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"09:40 PM"},"updated_at":"Dec 08, 2023","updated_at_time":1702014356,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_u