n India. The building offers premium office spaces for corporates, professionals, and entrepreneurs who want to work in a futuristic and vibrant environment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe building has state-of-the-art amenities and features, such as high-speed elevators, smart security systems, energy-efficient lighting, water harvesting, waste management, fire safety, and more. The building also has a sky lounge on the top floor, where the occupants can enjoy panoramic views of GIFT City and the surrounding landscape.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Conclusion</strong><br />\nShivalik Curv is not just a building, it is a vision. A vision to create a landmark that will showcase India&rsquo;s prowess in architecture and engineering. A vision to create a landmark that will attract global attention and admiration. A vision to create a landmark that will make every Indian proud.</p>\n\n<h4><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Group invites you to be a part of this vision. To own a space in Shivalik Curv is to own a piece of history. To own a space in Shivalik Curv is to own a piece of art. To own a space in Shivalik Curv is to own a piece of the future.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">- Piyush Golani</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"India’s Twisted Tower - Shivalik Curv","seo_description":"Shivalik Curv is a stunning skyscraper with a unique twisted shape in GIFT City. It offers premium office spaces with state-of-the-art amenities and features.","seo_keywords":"Curv, Twisted Tower, Landmark, Commercial Building, GIFT City, India","seo_image":"banner_1699435192_76.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1699435192_76.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Twisted Tower","tag_lower":"twisted tower"},{"text":"Landmark","tag_lower":"landmark"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"},{"text":"Commercial Bulding","tag_lower":"commercial bulding"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"},{"text":"Curv","tag_lower":"curv"}],"tags_array":["Twisted Tower","Landmark","GIFT City","Commercial Bulding","India","Curv"],"tags_commaseparted":"Twisted Tower,Landmark,GIFT City,Commercial Bulding,India,Curv","published_time":1699381800,"published_date":"08 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1699435066,"date_format":"","date_time":"02:47 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"08 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"02:47 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 08, 2023","updated_at_time":1699435238,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1699447665","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/decoding-the-perks-of-each-floor:-from-ground-to-skyline"},"id":231,"project_id":"174","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"decoding-the-perks-of-each-floor:-from-ground-to-skyline","image":"banner_1699427601_79.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1699427601_79.jpg","banner_title":"Decoding the Perks of Each Floor: From Ground to Skyline","title":"Decoding the Perks of Each Floor: From Ground to Skyline","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>The choice of floor selection in a building plays a pivotal role when a customer books a flat. Each floor offers a unique living experience, with a delicate balance of advantages and considerations. The first floor, easily accessible and reassuringly close to the entrance, may suit those valuing convenience and security. On the second floor, residents find a middle ground of accessibility and tranquillity. The upper floors have breathtaking views, reduced noise, ample natural light, and enhanced ventilation. Customers must carefully weigh these factors, as well as any pricing differences, to select the floor that harmonizes best with their lifestyle, needs, and personal preferences. The floor choice ultimately shapes not just their physical living space but also their overall living experience in the building.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nHere&rsquo;s a floor-wise description of the advantages and considerations when booking a flat in a multi-story building:</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>First Floor:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Accessibility: The first floor is the most accessible and convenient for those with elders and small children. It is very advantageous for those who want easy access without relying on elevators, which can also be helpful for individuals with mobility issues.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Safety</strong></p>\n\n<p>Some customers may feel more secure on the first floor as it is closer to the building&#39;s entrance.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Second &amp; Third Floor</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Middle ground</strong></p>\n\n<p>Easily reachable by stairs and elevator, making it convenient for most residents.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Balanced Noise</strong></p>\n\n<p>It&#39;s often quieter than the first floor but still provides easy access.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIt strikes a balance between being higher up and not too far from the ground. This can be ideal for those who want some of the benefits of elevation without being extremely high up. While it may require the use of an elevator or a short climb of stairs, it&#39;s usually more accessible than the uppermost floors, making it a practical choice for many residents, including those with mobility concerns.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Upper Floors (Fourth and Above)</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Views</strong></p>\n\n<p>Higher floors typically offer better views.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Less Noise</strong></p>\n\n<p>Upper floors tend to be quieter, away from street-level noises.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>More Natural Light</strong></p>\n\n<p>Increased sunlight due to height, provides a brighter living space.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Ventilation</strong></p>\n\n<p>Better air circulation on higher floors can enhance comfort.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Security</strong></p>\n\n<p>Some residents feel more secure on upper floors, as they are less accessible.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Considerations for Upper Floors</strong></p>\n\n<p>Elevator Dependency: You may need to rely on elevators for access, which could be a consideration during peak usage times.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nHence, lower floors, easily accessible and reassuringly may suit those valuing convenience and security. However, it&#39;s the upper floors that often steal the spotlight with breathtaking views, and reduced noise.</p>\n\n<h4><br />\n<br />\nIt&#39;s a decision that should be made thoughtfully, considering family preferences, priorities, and budget constraints, as it plays an influential role in defining one&#39;s daily life and comfort within the building.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-&nbsp;Hardi Shah</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Decoding the Perks of Each Floor: From Ground to Skyline","seo_description":"A floor guide line at Skyline.  The floor you choose in a multi-story building can significantly impact your daily life. The first floor offers unmatched accessibility and is perfect for those valuing convenience. It's also a safe bet for those with mobility concerns. On the second and third floors, you'll find a sweet spot with accessibility and tranquillity. It's a practical choice for most residents. However, the upper floors, from the fourth and above, boast stunning views, serenity, abundant natural light, and enhanced ventilation. Security is another perk. The choice ultimately shapes your living experience, so consider your lifestyle, needs, and preferences carefully.","seo_keywords":"Shivalik, Skyview, GIFT City, Real Estate, Ahmedabad, Innovation, Landmark","seo_image":"banner_1699426939_35.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1699426939_35.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Skyview","tag_lower":"skyview"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Drone Inspired Building","tag_lower":"drone inspired building"}],"tags_array":["Shivalik","Skyview","GIFT City","Real Estate","Ahmedabad","Drone Inspired Building"],"tags_commaseparted":"Shivalik,Skyview,GIFT City,Real Estate,Ahmedabad,Drone Inspired Building","published_time":1699209000,"published_date":"06 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1699261484,"date_format":"","date_time":"02:34 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"06 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"02:34 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 08, 2023","updated_at_time":1699427998,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1699428689","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/twisted-commercial-building-in-india:-a-new-trend-in-architecture."},"id":230,"project_id":"175","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"twisted-commercial-building-in-india:-a-new-trend-in-architecture.","image":"banner_1699018172_9.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1699018172_9.jpg","banner_title":"Twisted Commercial Building in India: A New Trend in Architecture","title":"Twisted Commercial Building in India: A New Trend in Architecture.","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-c32c8dc4-7fff-758d-7976-22236f6a9a3a\">Introduction</b><br />\n<br />\nHave you ever seen a building that looks like it is twisting or rotating? If you have, then you have witnessed a twisted commercial building, a new trend in architecture that is gaining popularity around the world.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nA twisted commercial building is a building that has a curved or twisted shape, rather than a straight or rectangular one. This design creates a dynamic and eye-catching appearance, as well as some practical and environmental benefits.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIn this blog, we will explore what makes a twisted commercial building so unique and attractive, and how it can enhance the value and performance of a commercial space.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe will also introduce you to Shivalik Curv, India&rsquo;s twisted tower, and how it is setting a new benchmark in architectural excellence and innovation.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>What is a Twisted Commercial Building?</strong></p>\n\n<p>A twisted commercial building is a building that has a non-linear shape, meaning that it does not follow a straight line or a right angle.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nInstead, it has a curved or twisted form, creating an impression of movement and dynamism. A twisted commercial building can have different degrees of twist, from subtle to dramatic, depending on the design and the purpose of the building.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nA twisted commercial building can be achieved by various methods, such as using different materials, angles, or structural systems. Some common techniques are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Using different floor plates or modules that rotate or shift along the height of the building</li>\n\t<li>Using diagonal columns or beams that support the twisting shape of the building</li>\n\t<li>Using curved glass panels or facades that create an illusion of twist</li>\n\t<li>Using prefabricated or modular units that can be assembled in different configurations<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Why Choose a Twisted Commercial Building?</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nA twisted commercial building is not just a visual spectacle, but also a smart choice for many reasons. Some of the advantages of choosing a twisted commercial building are:</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nAesthetic appeal: A twisted commercial building stands out from the crowd and creates a memorable impression on the viewers. It also reflects the creativity and vision of the architect and the owner of the building.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nFunctional efficiency: A twisted commercial building can optimize the use of space and light, as well as reduce wind loads and vibrations. By rotating or shifting the floor plates or modules, a twisted commercial building can create more floor area, more views, more natural light, and more ventilation for the occupants. By curving or twisting the shape of the building, a twisted commercial building can also reduce the impact of wind forces and seismic movements on the structure.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nEnvironmental sustainability: A twisted commercial building can also contribute to environmental sustainability by reducing energy consumption and carbon emissions. By maximizing natural light and ventilation, a twisted commercial building can lower the need for artificial lighting and cooling systems. By minimizing wind loads and vibrations, a twisted commercial building can also reduce the amount of material and reinforcement needed for the construction.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Examples of Twisted Commercial Buildings Around the World</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nTwisted commercial buildings are not a new phenomenon, but they have become more popular and prevalent in recent years. Some of the most famous examples of twisted commercial buildings around the world are:</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe Turning Torso: Located in Malmo, Sweden, this is one of the earliest and most iconic examples of twisted commercial buildings. Designed by Spanish architect Santiago Calatrava, this 190-meter tall tower consists of nine cubes that rotate 90 degrees from bottom to top. The tower houses offices, apartments, conference facilities, and a wellness center.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe Evolution Tower: Located in Moscow, Russia, this is one of the most elegant and graceful examples of twisted commercial buildings. Designed by British architect Tony Kettle, this 255-meter tall tower consists of 52 floors that twist 156 degrees from bottom to top. The tower houses offices, retail spaces, restaurants, and a fitness center.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe Shanghai Tower: Located in Shanghai, China, this is one of the tallest and most advanced examples of twisted commercial buildings. Designed by American architect Marshall Strabala, this 632-meter tall tower consists of 128 floors that twist 120 degrees from bottom to top. The tower houses offices, hotels, observation decks, and a museum.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Shivalik Curv: India&rsquo;s Twisted Tower</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nWhile twisted commercial buildings are becoming more common around the world, they are still rare and novel in India. However, that is about to change with the launch of Shivalik Curv, India&rsquo;s twisted tower.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Curv is a 32-storey green building that is located in the heart of the GIFT City, India&rsquo;s first smart city and international financial hub. Shivalik Curv is a project by Shivalik Group, one of the leading real estate developers in Gujarat, with a legacy of over 25 years.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Curv is not just a twisted commercial building, but a symbol of innovation and ambition.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIt is not just about height, but setting the sights on the city, that shapes and raises the standard in global markets. Shivalik Curv is a testament to India as this 32-storey building will be constructed with a combination of advanced technology and the latest architectural design.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Curv offers a range of premium commercial spaces, such as offices, showrooms, retail outlets, restaurants, and banquet halls. Shivalik Curv also provides a host of world-class amenities and facilities, such as high-speed elevators, 24/7 security, CCTV surveillance, fire safety systems, power backup, parking spaces, and more. Shivalik Curv also boasts of being a green building, with features such as rainwater harvesting, solar panels, waste management systems, and energy-efficient lighting and cooling systems.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Curv is not just a twisted commercial building, but a twisted commercial opportunity. It is an opportunity to own a piece of history and be part of India&rsquo;s twisted tower.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIt is an opportunity to elevate your business and brand image and be part of India&rsquo;s first smart city and international financial hub. It is an opportunity to enjoy the benefits of a twisted commercial building and be part of a new trend in architecture.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nTwisted commercial buildings are a new trend in architecture that combine aesthetics, functionality, and sustainability.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThey are buildings that have a curved or twisted shape, rather than a straight or rectangular one. They offer many advantages, such as visual appeal, functional efficiency, and environmental sustainability.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThey are also becoming more popular and prevalent around the world, with some famous examples being the Turning Torso in Sweden, the Evolution Tower in Russia, and the Shanghai Tower in China.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIndia&rsquo;s twisted tower is Shivalik Curv, a 32-storey green building that is located in the heart of the GIFT City. Shivalik Curv is a project by Shivalik Group, one of the leading real estate developers in Gujarat.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Curv offers premium commercial spaces and world-class amenities and facilities. Shivalik Curv is also a symbol of innovation and ambition, and a testament to India&rsquo;s architectural excellence and potential.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIf you are interested in owning or leasing a space in Shivalik Curv, India&rsquo;s twisted tower, please visit https://www.shivalikgroup.com/project/shivalik-curv or contact us at +91-79-4000-4000.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>FAQs</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. What is a twisted commercial building?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. twisted commercial building is a building that has a curved or twisted shape, rather than a straight or rectangular one.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. What are the benefits of choosing a twisted commercial building?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. Some of the benefits of choosing a twisted commercial building are aesthetic appeal, functional efficiency, and environmental sustainability.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. What are some examples of twisted commercial buildings around the world?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. Some examples of twisted commercial buildings around the world are the Turning Torso in Sweden, the Evolution Tower in Russia, and the Shanghai Tower in China.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. What is Shivalik Curv?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. Shivalik Curv is India&rsquo;s twisted tower, a 32-storey green building that is located in the heart of the GIFT City. It is a project by Shivalik Group, one of the leading real estate developers in Gujarat.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. What does Shivalik Curv offer?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. Shivalik Curv offers premium commercial spaces such as offices, showrooms, retail outlets, restaurants, and banquet halls. It also provides world-class amenities and facilities such as high-speed elevators, 24/7 security, CCTV surveillance, fire safety systems, power backup, parking spaces, and more.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. How can I own or lease a space in Shivalik Curv?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>A. You can own or lease a space in Shivalik Curv by visiting https://www.shivalikgroup.com/project/shivalik-curv or contacting us at +91-79-4000-4000.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-&nbsp;<strong dir=\"auto\">Piyush Golani</strong></span></p>\n","seo_title":"Twisted Commercial Building in India: A New Trend in Architecture | Shivalik Group","seo_description":"Learn about the twisted commercial building in India, a new trend in architecture that combines aesthetics, functionality, and sustainability. Discover how Shivalik Curv, India’s twisted tower, is leading the way in this innovative design.","seo_keywords":"Twisted Tower, India, Curv, Shivalik, GIFT City, Landmark, Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1699018276_43.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1699018276_43.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Twisted Tower","tag_lower":"twisted tower"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"},{"text":"Commercial","tag_lower":"commercial"},{"text":"Landmark","tag_lower":"landmark"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"}],"tags_array":["Twisted Tower","India","Commercial","Landmark","Shivalik","Ahmedabad","GIFT City"],"tags_commaseparted":"Twisted Tower,India,Commercial,Landmark,Shivalik,Ahmedabad,GIFT City","published_time":1698949800,"published_date":"03 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1699018173,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:59 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"03 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"06:59 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 08, 2023","updated_at_time":1699426520,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1699426559","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/why-does-ahmedabad-emerge-as-the-prime-choice-for-commercial-property-investment"},"id":228,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"why-does-ahmedabad-emerge-as-the-prime-choice-for-commercial-property-investment","image":"banner_1698991684_31.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698991684_31.jpg","banner_title":"Why does Ahmedabad Emerge as the Prime Choice for Commercial Property Investment?","title":"Why does Ahmedabad Emerge as the Prime Choice for Commercial Property Investment?","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>Ahmedabad, the bustling heart of Gujarat, stands as a thriving hub for trade and commerce, playing host to a wide array of sectors like engineering, chemicals, textiles, and automobiles. With its rapidly growing population of seven million, this UNESCO World Heritage City boasts a unique blend of modernity and ancient Indian traditions, making it an ideal investment destination.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nInvesting in Ahmedabad today, with its robust annual growth, promises to yield substantial returns in the future. The city&#39;s property market has witnessed a surge in sales, largely attributed to the implementation of the Real Estate (Regulation and Development) Act (RERA), drawing the attention of investors from across the nation.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nLet&#39;s delve into the factors that make this prosperous, eco-friendly city an excellent choice for real estate investment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Commercial Growth:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ahmedabad is experiencing an unprecedented boom in commercial development, a key driver of its real estate appeal. The city has witnessed the emergence of various industries such as BPOs, KPOs, IT companies, and international organizations, leading to an increase in demand for both residential and commercial properties. Investment in Ahmedabad&#39;s commercial real estate market promises a solid return on investment, driven in part by RERA compliance.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Investor-Friendly Atmosphere:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ahmedabad stands out as one of the few Indian cities offering both a friendly investment climate and a substantial investor base. The local real estate market, while not as expensive as in major metropolitan areas, offers affordable residential and commercial leasing options.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Rise in Economic Growth:</strong></p>\n\n<p>The proposed bullet train connecting Mumbai and Ahmedabad promises to provide quick and affordable access to the country&#39;s economic center. This infrastructure development will lead to increased economic activity, including more affordable housing, commercial spaces, and logistical centers along the train route. This, in turn, will stimulate the city&#39;s economy, attracting new businesses and investments, particularly from NRIs considering a future move to India.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Diverse Architecture:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ahmedabad&#39;s architectural landscape seamlessly blends ancient heritage with cutting-edge design, showcasing a unique juxtaposition of Mughal and contemporary styles. Notably, the Satellite Ahmedabad complex is gaining popularity due to its expanding potential, well-maintained infrastructure, and high inventory of properties, making it a compelling choice for investors.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Well-Built Infrastructure:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Ahmedabad&#39;s extensive road network has significantly contributed to the growing investor sentiment. Infrastructure improvements have facilitated the growth of surrounding areas and reduced traffic congestion. The city boasts efficient public transportation systems, including the metro and the Bus Rapid Transit System (BRTS), further enhancing connectivity. Reliable water and power supplies, along with lower business operational costs compared to other cities, make Ahmedabad an attractive choice for enterprises.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIn this landscape, Shivalik Highstreet, a project by the Shivalik Group, stands as a valuable resource for discovering commercial office space in Ahmedabad. Their team of real estate experts simplifies the process of finding the ideal commercial property, offering a wide range of options, from retail spaces to office rentals. Their commitment to delivering an exceptional experience ensures that you find precisely what you&#39;re looking for in Ahmedabad&#39;s dynamic real estate market.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><br />\n<span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">-&nbsp;Jayshree Ochwani</span></h4>\n","seo_title":"Why does Ahmedabad Emerge as the Prime Choice for Commercial Property Investment?","seo_description":"Discover the prime investment potential of Ahmedabad, a vibrant city in Gujarat, with a thriving commercial landscape. Explore the factors that make Ahmedabad the preferred choice for real estate investment, including its commercial growth, investor-friendly atmosphere, economic rise, diverse architecture, and well-built infrastructure. Unlock the opportunities with Shivalik Highstreet, offering a range of commercial properties, from retail spaces to office rentals, simplifying your journey in Ahmedabad's dynamic real estate market. Invest wisely in this bustling hub of trade and commerce.","seo_keywords":"Real Estate, Ahmedabad, Commercial Properties, Shivalik, Highstreet","seo_image":"banner_1698991895_7.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1698991895_7.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Commercial Property","tag_lower":"commercial property"},{"text":"Commercial","tag_lower":"commercial"}],"tags_array":["Ahmedabad","Real Estate","Commercial Property","Commercial"],"tags_commaseparted":"Ahmedabad,Real Estate,Commercial Property,Commercial","published_time":1698863400,"published_date":"02 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1698991685,"date_format":"","date_time":"11:38 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"03 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"11:38 AM"},"updated_at":"Nov 03, 2023","updated_at_time":1698992148,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1698992632","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/shivalik-highstreet:-revolutionizing-urban-design"},"id":226,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"shivalik-highstreet:-revolutionizing-urban-design","image":"banner_1698847952_50.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698847952_50.jpg","banner_title":"Shivalik Highstreet: Revolutionizing Urban Design","title":"Shivalik Highstreet: Revolutionizing Urban Design","description":"<p>Ahmedabad, a city in western India, has a rich history and culture. Over the years, it has undergone significant changes and evolved into a modern metropolis. One of the areas that has witnessed this transformation is Bodakdev, an upscale locality in the city. The Shivalik Highstreet project by the Shivalik Group is one of the architectural gems in this area. The project&#39;s design is visually stunning but also serves as a social hub for people.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Paradigm Shift in Urban Design</strong><br />\nShivalik Highstreet transcends the definition of a commercial complex; it stands as a testament to pioneering urban design. The Shivalik Group, renowned for its commitment to quality and excellence, embarked on this project to create something extraordinary. Their vision was not just to cater to the city&#39;s lifestyle needs but to etch an indelible mark on its architectural landscape.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Unconventional and Innovative Design</strong><br />\nThe design of Shivalik Highstreet is unparalleled in Ahmedabad and India as a whole. Its most striking feature is the &quot;Namstey&quot; (a traditional Indian greeting) shaped building that symbolizes welcome and inclusivity. The concept was conceived by architects and designers who aimed to shatter conventional architectural norms and create a landmark that celebrated Indian culture and values.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>An Ideation</strong><br />\nThe idea behind Shivalik Highstreet had a threefold purpose: to create something unique, to transform the city&#39;s skyline, and, most importantly, to extend a warm welcome to all.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Let&#39;s explore each facet in depth:</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Creating Something Unique</strong><br />\nIn a world filled with cookie-cutter buildings and shopping complexes, Shivalik Group sought to provide an unparalleled experience. The choice of the &quot;Namstey&quot; design went beyond aesthetics; it held cultural significance. This design is an invitation, a warm embrace for all visitors, and a reminder of the rich Indian heritage that thrives in the heart of modern Ahmedabad.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Changing the City&#39;s Skyline</strong><br />\nWhile Ahmedabad has experienced rapid urban development, Shivalik Highstreet elevated it to the next level. The distinctive shape of the building has become an iconic feature of the city&#39;s skyline. It symbolizes the city&#39;s progress and forward-thinking spirit, serving as a testament to Ahmedabad&#39;s readiness to embrace innovation.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Welcoming Everyone to Our City</strong><br />\nThe shape of Shivalik Highstreet goes beyond aesthetics; it conveys a profound message of welcome. It embodies Ahmedabad&#39;s spirit&mdash;a city known for its warmth, inclusivity, and hospitality. Shivalik Group intended to create a space where individuals from diverse backgrounds could come together, feel at home, and enjoy all that the complex offers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Conclusion</strong><br />\nShivalik Highstreet is a commercial complex located in Bodakdev, Ahmedabad, that stands out as an architectural masterpiece. It&#39;s not just a regular building, but an embodiment of the Shivalik Group&#39;s vision to create something unique, redefine the city&#39;s skyline, and extend a warm welcome to Ahmedabad. With its grandeur and innovative design, Shivalik Highstreet has become a symbol of welcome and an inspiration for other commercial developments in the city.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#bdc3c7;\">- Jayshree Ochwani</span></h5>\n","seo_title":"Shivalik Highstreet: Revolutionizing Urban Design","seo_description":"Shivalik Highstreet changed the skyline of Ahmedabad city with its innovative and unique design. The Namstey shaped building by Shivalik stands tall to greet & welcome everyone to city.","seo_keywords":"Shivalik Highstreet, Namstey-Shaped Building, Innovation, Unique Design","seo_image":"banner_1698848008_1.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1698848008_1.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Shivalik Highstreet","tag_lower":"shivalik highstreet"},{"text":"Namstey-Shaped Building","tag_lower":"namstey-shaped building"},{"text":"Innovation","tag_lower":"innovation"},{"text":"Unique Design","tag_lower":"unique design"}],"tags_array":["Shivalik Highstreet","Namstey-Shaped Building","Innovation","Unique Design"],"tags_commaseparted":"Shivalik Highstreet,Namstey-Shaped Building,Innovation,Unique Design","published_time":1698777000,"published_date":"01 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1698847952,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:42 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"01 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"07:42 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 01, 2023","updated_at_time":1698848018,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"209","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1698991968","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"Aakash","added_by_type":"sales executive"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/the-significance-of-3d-visualization-in-interior-design"},"id":225,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"8","slug":"the-significance-of-3d-visualization-in-interior-design","image":"banner_1698839626_46.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698839626_46.jpeg","banner_title":"The Significance of 3D Visualization in Interior Design","title":"The Significance of 3D Visualization in Interior Design","description":"<p>Do you dream of the perfect home, complete with a cozy living room, your dream kitchen, and a bedroom that feels like a retreat? Imagine stepping into your dream space before it&#39;s even constructed. Thanks to the wonders of 3D visualization, your dreams can now become a reality. In this blog, we&#39;ll explore the importance of 3D visualization and how it can revolutionize the way you plan and design your home.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nVisualizing the Unseen:<br />\nOne of the most significant benefits of 3D visualization is its ability to bring your interior design concepts to life. Before 3D visualization, homeowners relied on blueprints and sketches to understand what their future homes might look like. However, with 3D visualization, you can explore every corner of your home in vivid detail. It&#39;s like taking a virtual tour of your home-to-be, long before construction begins.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nEliminating Surprises:<br />\nSurprises are rarely welcome in home design and construction. 3D visualization helps eliminate these surprises by allowing you to see the final look of your home in advance. You can make changes and adjustments to the design until it matches your vision. This means no unexpected layout issues or design regrets.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nInformed Decision-Making:<br />\n3D visualization allows you to make informed decisions about your interior design. You can experiment with different colour schemes, furniture arrangements, and finishes. It&#39;s like having a paintbrush and palette to create your masterpiece. You can see how your choices impact the overall look of your home, helping you create a space that genuinely reflects your style and personality.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nSaving Time and Money:<br />\nOne of the most practical aspects of 3D visualization is its ability to save you time and money. By identifying potential design flaws or issues early on, you can avoid costly changes during construction. This results in fewer delays, fewer budget overruns, and a smoother building process.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nEffective Communication:<br />\n3D visualization acts as a universal language that bridges the communication gap between you and the professionals working on your project. It ensures that everyone understands your vision, facilitating effective collaboration and a successful outcome.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nA Sense of Anticipation:<br />\nAnother exciting aspect of 3D visualization is that it adds an element of anticipation to the home-building process. You can get a glimpse of your future home and build excitement for the day you move in. It&#39;s like opening a present before the big day arrives.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nIn Closing!<br />\n3D visualization is a game-changer in the world of interior design and home construction. It provides a clear, detailed, and immersive way to see how your home will appear in the future. It eliminates surprises, saves time and money, and enhances effective communication throughout the design and construction process.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nSo, if you&#39;re planning to build your dream home, make sure to consider the advantages of 3D visualization. It&#39;s the key to bringing your dreams to life, one pixel at a time. Get ready to step into your dream space and watch your home transform from imagination to reality!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color:#999999;\">-<span style=\"background-color:#000000;\">Jayshree Ochwani</span></span></p>\n","seo_title":"The Significance of 3D Visualization in Interior Design","seo_description":"3D visualization in interior design is very important. With wonders of 3D visualization, your dreams can now become a reality.","seo_keywords":"interior design","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Interior","tag_lower":"interior"}],"tags_array":["Interior"],"tags_commaseparted":"Interior","published_time":1698777000,"published_date":"01 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":1698839626,"date_format":"","date_time":"05:23 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"01 Nov, 2023","created_at_time":"05:23 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 03, 2023","updated_at_time":1698993145,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"0","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1698993156","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/how-does-shivalik-group’s-payment-plan-10:75:15-benefit-homebuyers"},"id":222,"project_id":"4","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"how-does-shivalik-group’s-payment-plan-10:75:15-benefit-homebuyers","image":"banner_1698671901_6.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698671901_6.jpg","banner_title":"How Does Shivalik Group’s Payment Plan 10:75:15 Benefit Homebuyers?","title":"How Does Shivalik Group’s Payment Plan 10:75:15 Benefit Homebuyers?","description":"<p>As one of the leading developers in the real estate sector, Shivalik Group has consistently delivered excellence and quality to its customers. Customers are at the center of everything Shivalik Group does, making it a trusted choice in Ahmedabad real estate.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nOne common point that has been analyzed when customers buy homes is the challenge of managing their finances. Many homebuyers face the burden of having to manage the entire fund upfront, along with ongoing monthly EMIs.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nAs a solution to this problem - Shivalik Group has introduced a customer-centric payment plan referred to as the - 10:75:15 plan.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nWe have already implemented this payment plan in Shivalik Sharda Harmony and The Crown. Many homebuyers appreciate the thoughtful and customer-friendly approach and we have received an overwhelmingly positive response.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nHere are the details of this approach that is intended to make the dream of homeownership more convenient and stress-free.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>What is the 10:75:15 Payment Plan?</strong><br />\nThe 10:75:15 payment plan is a thoughtful solution to ease the financial stress of home ownership. This is how it works:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 10% as a Token</strong><br />\nTo begin your home-buying journey, you only need to pay 10%. Taking this first step allows you to secure your dream home without making a large upfront payment.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 75% Loan with EMI after Possession</strong><br />\n75% of the total amount is covered by a loan, with EMI payments beginning after possession. In this way, you don&#39;t have to worry about EMI payments until you move into your new home.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 15% Due Upon Possession</strong><br />\nYou will pay 15% upon taking possession of your new home. Taking this phased approach to payments ensures a smooth and stress-free buying experience, allowing you to settle in easily.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>What Are the Benefits of This Payment Plan?</strong><br />\nA key feature of the 10:75:15 plan is that there are no interest or home loans until possession.</p>\n\n<p>Consider this scenario - with a traditional home loan at 9% interest for Rs. 1 crore over 30 years, you would pay Rs. 9.65 lacs in interest every year. In the 10:75:15 plan, you&#39;ll have no interest payments or home loan obligations until you take possession of your new home.</p>\n\n<p>In practical terms, this means substantial savings. Depending on the possession timeline, you could easily save Rs. 20-30 lacs by avoiding interest payments during the pre-possession period.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Also, those who live in rented houses benefit from this plan since EMIs don&#39;t start until they get possession, so they don&#39;t have to worry about managing both.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Group is planning to extend the same transparent and hassle-free payment plan to its upcoming projects.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Get in touch with Shivalik Group to learn more about this innovative payment plan and to find your dream home.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>- Kishan Thakkar</p>\n","seo_title":"How Does Shivalik Group’s Payment Plan 10:75:15 Benefit Homebuyers?","seo_description":"Learn about Shivalik Group's payment plan 10:75:15 and its advantages for homebuyers in this article. Find out more about this plan!","seo_keywords":"Payment Plan Harmony Shivalik Real Estate  Ahmedabad","seo_image":"banner_1698755445_76.jpg","seo_image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/seo/banner_1698755445_76.jpg","tags":[{"text":"Payment Plan","tag_lower":"payment plan"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Harmony","tag_lower":"harmony"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"}],"tags_array":["Payment Plan","Shivalik","Harmony","Ahmedabad","Real Estate"],"tags_commaseparted":"Payment Plan,Shivalik,Harmony,Ahmedabad,Real Estate","published_time":1698604200,"published_date":"30 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698671901,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:48 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"30 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"06:48 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 31, 2023","updated_at_time":1698755455,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1698823035","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/launching-shivalik-curv:-a-smart-investment-in-gift-city"},"id":219,"project_id":"175","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"launching-shivalik-curv:-a-smart-investment-in-gift-city","image":"banner_1698420236_53.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698420236_53.jpg","banner_title":"Launching Shivalik CURV: A Smart Investment in GIFT City","title":"Launching Shivalik CURV: A Smart Investment in GIFT City","description":"<p>Shivalik CURV is a prestigious commercial project in the heart of GIFT City, offering modern office spaces, showrooms, and retail spaces. Explore its potential for capital appreciation, high rental income, and tax benefits.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe have just received RERA for Shivalik Curv. This will be the Twisted Commercial Landmark of India. It will put GIFT City on the World Map.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>GIFT City, rapidly emerging as a prominent financial hub in India, presents an unparalleled<br />\ninvestment opportunity with &amp; quot; Shivalik CURV,&amp;quot; a strategically positioned commercial project.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNestled at the heart of GIFT City, adjacent to the iconic GIFT Tower and GIFT Club, Shivalik CURV enjoys seamless connectivity through major highways and public transportation<br />\nnetworks.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCURV boasts an array of commercial spaces, including cutting-edge office spaces, spacious showrooms, and prime retail spaces. Its office spaces epitomize modernity and efficiency, featuring high ceilings, abundant natural light, and state-of-the-art amenities. The generously lit and spacious showrooms cater to businesses seeking to showcase their products and services. The ground-floor retail spaces, strategically located, are tailor-made to attract a steady stream of foot traffic.<br />\n<br />\nBeyond its prime location and contemporary amenities, CURV offers a suite of<br />\ncompelling benefits for investors, including:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Potential for Capital Appreciation</strong><br />\n<br />\nIn one of India&#39;s&nbsp;fastest-growing areas, CURV is poised for substantial capital appreciation in the years ahead.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>High Rental Income</strong><br />\n<br />\nCURV enjoys a premium commercial address surrounded by businesses of all scales, ensuring consistent demand for office, showroom, and retail space. Investors can expect a lucrative rental income.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tax Benefits</strong><br />\nGIFT City offers attractive tax incentives, including reduced property taxes and exemptions from capital gains tax. These incentives significantly enhance the overall investment appeal of CURV.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe CURV is a prudent investment choice for those seeking to leverage the growth of GIFT City. The project combines a prime location, modern amenities, substantial capital appreciation potential, and robust rental income prospects. If you aspire to nurture your wealth, The Curv is a compelling option.<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Here are additional reasons to consider The CURV in GIFT City</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Reputed Developer</strong><br />\nDeveloped by Shivalik Group, a distinguished name in Indian real estate known for delivering quality projects, CURV offers the assurance of a secure investment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>World-renowned Architects</strong><br />\nA globally acclaimed team that curates The CURV&#39;s&nbsp;design, ensuring a perfect blend of aesthetics and functionality poised for enduring value appreciation.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Highest Standards</strong><br />\nCURV adheres to the highest quality and safety standards, safeguarding your investment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Unique Design</strong><br />\nThe CURV offers wide office spaces with scenic views of the riverfront and the skyline of GIFT City. It is a modern office complex with a curved design that offers stunning city views.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nFor astute investors seeking a wise investment opportunity within GIFT City, CURV represents an optimal choice.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- Khushbu Raval</p>\n","seo_title":"Launching Shivalik CURV: A Smart Investment in GIFT City","seo_description":"Shivalik CURV is a prestigious commercial project in the heart of GIFT City, offering modern office spaces, showrooms, and retail spaces. Explore its potential for capital appreciation, high rental income, and tax benefits.","seo_keywords":"Curv, Twisted Tower, Landmark, Shivalik, GIFT City, India Real Estate","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Cruv","tag_lower":"cruv"},{"text":"Twisted Tower","tag_lower":"twisted tower"},{"text":"Landmark","tag_lower":"landmark"},{"text":"India","tag_lower":"india"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"}],"tags_array":["Cruv","Twisted Tower","Landmark","India","Real Estate","GIFT City"],"tags_commaseparted":"Cruv,Twisted Tower,Landmark,India,Real Estate,GIFT City","published_time":1698345000,"published_date":"27 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698420236,"date_format":"","date_time":"08:53 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"27 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"08:53 PM"},"updated_at":"Nov 04, 2023","updated_at_time":1699095116,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"1699095125","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/how-to-finance-land-investment:-a-comprehensive-guide"},"id":218,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"how-to-finance-land-investment:-a-comprehensive-guide","image":"banner_1698405961_3.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698405961_3.jpg","banner_title":"How to Finance Land Investment: A Comprehensive Guide","title":"How to Finance Land Investment: A Comprehensive Guide","description":"<p>Land investment can be a lucrative endeavor, offering the potential for long-term appreciation and stability. However, securing financing for land investment can be a complex process, requiring careful planning and consideration.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nSmart investors understand the nuances of land financing and leverage a variety of strategies to secure the best possible terms and conditions. Here is a sophisticated guide to financing a land investment:</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Evaluate Your Investment Goals and Risk Tolerance</strong><br />\n<br />\nBefore exploring financing options, it is essential to have a clear understanding of your investment goals and risk tolerance. What is your intended use for the land? Are you looking to develop the land, hold it for appreciation, or both? Once you have a clear understanding of your goals, you can assess your risk tolerance and determine how much leverage you are comfortable with.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Explore Traditional and Non-Traditional Financing Options</strong><br />\n<br />\nTraditional lenders, such as banks and credit unions, offer a variety of loan products for land purchases. However, they may have strict credit score and debt-to-income ratio requirements. Sophisticated investors often explore non-traditional financing options, such as private lenders, hard money loans, and crowdfunding platforms. These options may be more flexible, but they may also come with higher interest rates and shorter repayment terms.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Structure Your Financing to Optimize Tax Benefits</strong><br />\n<br />\nLand investment can offer several tax benefits, such as capital gains tax deductions and depreciation deductions. Sophisticated investors carefully structure their financing to maximize these tax benefits. For example, they may use debt financing to purchase the land and equity financing to finance development costs. This can help to reduce their taxable income and increase their overall returns.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Mitigate Risk with Diversification</strong><br />\n<br />\nWise investors understand the importance of diversification. This means spreading your investment across different asset classes and sectors to reduce your overall risk. When financing a land investment, you can mitigate risk by diversifying your funding sources and investing in a variety of land parcels.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Work with Experienced Professionals</strong><br />\n<br />\nLand investment can be a complex undertaking, and it is important to work with experienced professionals throughout the process. This includes financial advisors, attorneys, and real estate professionals. Experienced professionals can help you assess your investment goals, explore financing options, and structure your transaction to optimize your returns and mitigate risk.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n<p>By following these well-thought-out strategies, you can increase your chances of success when financing a land investment. Remember, always seek professional financial advice before making any significant investment decisions.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-&nbsp;Khushbu Raval</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Land","tag_lower":"land"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"}],"tags_array":["Land","Real Estate","Shivalik","Investment"],"tags_commaseparted":"Land,Real Estate,Shivalik,Investment","published_time":1698258600,"published_date":"26 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698336051,"date_format":"","date_time":"09:30 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"26 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"09:30 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 27, 2023","updated_at_time":1698405961,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/how-shivalik-group-has-changed-the-skyline-of-ahmedabad"},"id":213,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"how-shivalik-group-has-changed-the-skyline-of-ahmedabad","image":"banner_1698247228_54.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698247228_54.jpg","banner_title":"How Shivalik Group Has Changed the Skyline of Ahmedabad","title":"How Shivalik Group Has Changed the Skyline of Ahmedabad","description":"<p>Ahmedabad has experienced rapid development over the past few decades, with skyscrapers, malls, and other urban developments built all over the city. The Shivalik Group played a significant role in changing the city&#39;s skyline.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nLet&#39;s look at the role the Shivalik Group played in changing the skyline.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nSince its foundation, Shivalik Group has been a pioneer in the real estate industry, leaving a significant mark on the landscape of the city.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWith over 25 years of experience in the real estate industry, the Shivalik Group has consistently delivered architectural wonders that are more than just structures but works of art that contribute to the city&#39;s skyline.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nAhmedabad locals always get captured by the buildings of Shivalik Group, be it Shivalik Shilp or Shivalik Highstreet. It gives the area - its own identity.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nListed below are some of the many projects that have contributed to drastically changing the skyline of the city. From luxury residential developments to contemporary commercial complexes, Shivalik Group has left a distinctive mark on Ahmedabad.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Shivalik Highstreet</strong></p>\n\n<p>With its shape of a &#39;Namaste,&#39; Shivalik High Street symbolizes both tradition and modernity, located at Judges Bungalow Road, Ahmedabad.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With eleven stories of premium business spaces, the building&#39;s modern architecture, characterized by a pervasive glazed fa&ccedil;ade, adds a dynamic touch.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Shivalik Shilp</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\nShivalik Shilp is a boat-shaped building located at Iscon Cross Road, it is Ahmedabad&#39;s most iconic and recognizable building. It not only stands as a structural marvel but also stands out among the rest of the buildings on Iscon Cross Road and has created a unique identity for the area.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Upcoming Projects at GIFT City</strong></p>\n\n<p>We are coming up with 2 more projects at GIFT City. Residential project with a drone-inspired shape, providing residents with an open and clear view of their surroundings &amp; The Curv, GIFT City&#39;s most unique project, The Curv is a unique commercial development with a distinctive curved shape.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Aside from adding aesthetic appeal and creating a unique skyline for GIFT City, this design also reflects Shivalik Group&#39;s innovative approach to architecture.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Shivalik Abaise</strong></p>\n\n<p>Located at Prahladnagar, Ahmedabad, the Shivalik Abaise building is a rocket-shaped structure with sharp inward inclinations. Its innovative design creates an impactful presence while opening up surrounding spaces.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Impact on the City&#39;s Economy and Lifestyle</strong></p>\n\n<p>The impact of Shivalik Group&#39;s projects extends well beyond architectural design. A number of these projects have contributed to the growth of local economies in particular areas or segments of those areas.</p>\n\n<p>Moreover, the lifestyle of residents near Shivalik Group&#39;s projects has transformed, with enhanced amenities and a more vibrant community atmosphere.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Make Tomorrow Better With Shivalik Group</strong></p>\n\n<p>It is not just structures that shape the skyline of a city, but also innovation, sustainability, and social development. The Shivalik Group is where every creation is a masterpiece, and every building contributes to Ahmedabad&#39;s unique culture.</p>\n\n<p>Ready to experience the future of living? Connect with Shivalik Group and be a part of the future skyline.</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Skyline","tag_lower":"skyline"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Gift City","tag_lower":"gift city"}],"tags_array":["Shivalik","Skyline","Real Estate","Ahmedabad","Gift City"],"tags_commaseparted":"Shivalik,Skyline,Real Estate,Ahmedabad,Gift City","published_time":1698172200,"published_date":"25 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698247229,"date_format":"","date_time":"08:50 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"25 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"08:50 PM"},"updated_at":"","updated_at_time":"","is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/the-impact-of-indian-real-estate:-a-holiday-special"},"id":211,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"the-impact-of-indian-real-estate:-a-holiday-special","image":"banner_1698210216_21.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698210216_21.jpg","banner_title":"The Impact of Indian Real Estate: A Holiday Special","title":"The Impact of Indian Real Estate: A Holiday Special","description":"<p>The real estate market has always been a dynamic and ever-evolving industry, shaped by economic developments, technological advances, and changing customer preferences. As the holiday season approaches, historically a period of heightened real estate activity, it&#39;s essential to delve deeper into what the market holds in store. Let&#39;s explore the fascinating world of real estate as we gear up for the holiday season, from emerging trends to innovative strategies.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIn India, the festive season signifies more than just celebration; it&#39;s a time of increased vibrancy and potential in the real estate market, making it an ideal time for investment. Festivals like Navratras, Dussehra, Dhanteras, and Diwali, symbolizing fresh beginnings and prosperity, typically witness a substantial surge in housing purchases. Market participants seize this opportunity to create an inviting atmosphere, often offering enticing discounts and significant incentives, thereby invigorating the real estate industry.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThis annual peak in business activity includes a slew of new projects and a range of incentives designed to attract homebuyers. During this season, the heightened demand for homes often translates into actual purchases, as prospective buyers are more likely to turn their dreams into reality, emphasizing stability and security, further fueling the demand for residential properties.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nDespite current home loan interest rates, demand for housing continues to show surprising resilience due to the affordability of the market. Homebuyers are not merely interested; they are enthusiastic about finalizing their real estate purchases during this auspicious season, underscoring the shift towards committed buyers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nAccording to recent estimates, the housing real estate sector experienced a substantial upswing during FYQ3 2022, with 88,230 dwelling units sold in the top seven cities&mdash;a remarkable 4% increase from the previous quarter and an impressive 41% increase from 2021. These figures indicate a 20% rise in sales during Q3, which corresponds to the holiday season in 2023. What sets today&#39;s housing demand apart is that even millennials view real estate as the most desirable asset class. The industry is balanced for a promising future, buoyed by improved consumer confidence and a thriving market. This expansion aligns with the growth of the corporate landscape and the increasing demand for enhanced lifestyles and housing options. The property market currently enjoys increased home purchasing activity, driven by end-user preferences and supported by higher savings and market stability.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nHomeownership offers tax benefits, including deductions for mortgage interest and property taxes, making it a prudent financial decision. Early-year government initiatives will further encourage millennials to invest in real estate, making homeownership more accessible during this holiday season. Year-end bonuses or cash gifts add to the allure, making homeownership an attractive option for millennials interested in real estate investing.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nIn conclusion, the resurgence of market enthusiasm amid a backdrop of robust economic activity makes the holiday season an opportunity for real estate investment. The revival of the real estate industry signals economic recovery and prosperity. With cautious optimism, this holiday season has the potential to provide a much-needed boost to the real estate sector.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-Jayshree Ochwani</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Festival","tag_lower":"festival"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Holiday","tag_lower":"holiday"}],"tags_array":["Festival","Real Estate","Shivalik","Holiday"],"tags_commaseparted":"Festival,Real Estate,Shivalik,Holiday","published_time":1698172200,"published_date":"25 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698210217,"date_format":"","date_time":"10:33 AM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"25 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"10:33 AM"},"updated_at":"Oct 25, 2023","updated_at_time":1698215572,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/navratri-property-deals:-the-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-real-estate"},"id":210,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"navratri-property-deals:-the-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-real-estate","image":"banner_1698045888_7.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1698045888_7.jpg","banner_title":"Navratri : The Best Time to Buy and Sell Real Estate","title":"Navratri Property Deals: The Best Time to Buy and Sell Real Estate","description":"<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>In India, the nine-night festival of Navratri, which is observed with great zeal and devotion, has great cultural significance. Navratri offers a special window of opportunity for people interested in real estate transactions, in addition to traditional dancing and prayer. The tenth day of Navratri, Dussehra, falls during this month, which is particularly auspicious for real estate transactions. Here&#39;s why the greatest time to buy real estate is around Navratri, which culminates in a big celebration on Dussehra.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Auspicious Beginnings</strong><br />\nNavratri signifies fresh starts, and buying a new home is the ideal way to make a fresh start. It&#39;s a fortunate moment for homebuyers to start a new chapter with a new residence. For sellers, it&#39;s a chance to start over by finalising a transaction and advancing financially.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Festival of Prosperity</strong><br />\nNavratri is all about celebrating prosperity and abundance. This theme resonates perfectly with real estate investments, which are seen as long-term wealth-building assets.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Spiritual Significance of Dussehra</strong><br />\nThe last day of Navratri, Dussehra, represents the victory of good over evil. It might be viewed as an opportunity for real estate buyers to overcome uncertainty by selecting a prudent investment. Sellers may see it as a chance to start over by getting rid of negative energy and stagnant real estate.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Community and Neighbourhood&nbsp;Vibrancy</strong><br />\nNavratri brings communities together in celebration. It&#39;s an opportunity for buyers to experience the vibrancy of neighbourhoods and envision themselves as part of the community, which can be a significant factor in property selection.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe happy celebration of Dussehra, which follows Navratri, provides a great setting for real estate purchases. Property deals are made more special by the combination of spiritual importance, joyful celebration, and auspicious beginnings. Navratri offers a great chance to convert this festival into a real estate celebration for both buyers and sellers. Take advantage of this auspicious time to buy or sell real estate by embracing the spirit of the season and making sure your investment path is in line with the benefits and positivity of Navratri.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- Bhavya Shah</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Navratri","tag_lower":"navratri"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"}],"tags_array":["Navratri","Real Estate"],"tags_commaseparted":"Navratri,Real Estate","published_time":1697999400,"published_date":"23 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1698045314,"date_format":"","date_time":"12:45 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"23 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"12:45 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 23, 2023","updated_at_time":1698045889,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/the-marketing-strategies:-analyzing-the-promotional-campaigns-and-strategies-used-by-shivalik-group-for-the-project."},"id":207,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"the-marketing-strategies:-analyzing-the-promotional-campaigns-and-strategies-used-by-shivalik-group-for-the-project.","image":"banner_1697698908_94.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1697698908_94.jpg","banner_title":"The Marketing Strategies","title":"The Marketing Strategies: Analyzing the promotional campaigns and strategies used by Shivalik Group for the project.","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>&quot;Quality speaks for itself&quot; is a core principle that has rooted the foundation of Shivalik Group for the last 25 years. In the ever-evolving landscape of the real estate industry, where competition is at its peak, the success of a project is often measured not only by bricks and mortar but also by its marketing strategies.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom towering hoardings that dominate the urban skyline to the inked pages of newspapers that have been a trusted source of information for generations, Shivalik Group&#39;s approach to marketing is a symphony of traditional and contemporary methods. But their marketing goes beyond the tangible. Shivalik Group has mastered creating organic leads. These leads aren&#39;t just numbers on a spreadsheet but their hard work for the last 25 years.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Word of Mouth - The Ultimate Testimony</strong></p>\n\n<p>In the world of real estate, there is no more incredible testament to a developer&#39;s success than word of mouth. The most compelling chapter in this story is written by their customers, who have become the ultimate advocates for the Shivalik Group.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Organic Leads - Building Trust</strong></p>\n\n<p>Building organic leads is a testament to Shivalik Group&#39;s commitment to quality and innovation. Their projects speak for themselves, attracting potential buyers genuinely interested in their offerings. By consistently delivering on promises, Shivalik Group has cultivated a loyal customer base that generates leads through word of mouth.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>The Power of Social Media:</strong></p>\n\n<p>In addition to its traditional marketing efforts, Shivalik Group has harnessed the power of social media to connect with its target audience. Their social media presence is a virtual window into their world of innovation and excellence. Here, they engage with their community, share glimpses of their projects, and foster a sense of belonging among their followers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Hoardings - Catching the Eye</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Group understands the importance of visibility. These eye-catching displays often feature unique designs and compelling visuals, creating a buzz in the market.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Newspaper Advertisements - A Trusted Source</strong></p>\n\n<p>For decades, newspapers have been a reliable source of information. Shivalik Group&#39;s marketing strategy includes newspaper advertisements that reach a broad audience. These ads highlight the quality and innovation of their projects, ensuring that the message resonates with previous clients and organic leads.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Unique Designs - Setting Trends</strong></p>\n\n<p>One of the cornerstones of Shivalik Group&#39;s marketing strategy is its emphasis on unique designs. Their innovative architecture and interior design approach create a distinct identity for each project. These unique designs not only attract potential buyers but also set trends in the industry.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Green Building - A Sustainable Choice</strong></p>\n\n<p>The Shivalik Group supports green building methods for increased environmental awareness. Their projects incorporate sustainable features, appealing to a target audience that values eco-friendly living.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nShivalik Group has always succeeded in introducing innovative features and amenities in their projects, catering to the evolving needs of their target audience. It&#39;s a story that unfolds like a series of carefully crafted chapters, each building upon the success of the previous one. At the heart of this narrative lies the remarkable journey from Shivalik Sharda Park View 1 to Shivalik Sharda Park View 2. Their commitment to excellence and innovation continues to set them apart in the industry, making them a name to watch in real estate.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-&nbsp;Nidhi Raikundaliya</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Marketing","tag_lower":"marketing"},{"text":"Shivalik","tag_lower":"shivalik"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Strategies","tag_lower":"strategies"}],"tags_array":["Marketing","Shivalik","Real Estate","Strategies"],"tags_commaseparted":"Marketing,Shivalik,Real Estate,Strategies","published_time":1697653800,"published_date":"19 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1697698909,"date_format":"","date_time":"12:31 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"19 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"12:31 PM"},"updated_at":"","updated_at_time":"","is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/investing-in-real-estate:-why-shivalik-group-is-the-best-choice"},"id":205,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"investing-in-real-estate:-why-shivalik-group-is-the-best-choice","image":"banner_1697465637_31.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1697465637_31.jpg","banner_title":"Investing in Real Estate: Why Shivalik Group Is the Best Choice","title":"Investing in Real Estate: Why Shivalik Group Is the Best Choice","description":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\n\n<p>If you&#39;re looking for a home in Ahmedabad, you&#39;ve certainly heard of Shivalik Group. Shivalik Group has been a key player in the real estate sector since 1998, leaving an indelible mark on the skyline of Ahmedabad.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With our timeless design, luxurious amenities, and sustainable living, we set ourselves apart from the competition.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Group is synonymous with excellence in the real estate industry,&nbsp;spearheading several projects across the city.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>7 Reasons to Choose Shivalik Group When It Comes to Investing or Buying a Home</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>A Renowned Name in the Real Estate Industry</strong></p>\n\n<p>Reputation matters in real estate, and Shivalik Group has earned a stellar reputation. Trusted and respected, investing with a renowned name ensures reliability and credibility in your property transactions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Buildings in Prime Locations</strong></p>\n\n<p>Shivalik Group strategically selects prime project locations, ensuring you live in an area with convenience, growth potential, and everything nearby.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Higher ROI For You</strong></p>\n\n<p>Investing with Shivalik Group isn&#39;t just about buying a property; it&#39;s a wise investment. The properties consistently yield higher returns, making it a lucrative investment opportunity.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Taking a Greener Approach to Buildings</strong></p>\n\n<p>In an era where sustainability matters, Shivalik Group takes the lead with green building practices. Your investment secures your future and contributes to a greener, more sustainable society.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Architectural Designs That Stand Out</strong></p>\n\n<p>A Shivalik Group home is more than just a house; it is an impressive piece of architecture. Each project reflects innovation, creativity, and a commitment to pushing the boundaries of traditional design.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Amenities to Enhance Your Lifestyle</strong></p>\n\n<p>Elevate your lifestyle with the luxurious amenities offered by Shivalik Group. From state-of-the-art fitness centres to serene landscaped gardens, your investment comes with an added layer of comfort and luxurious features.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Providing High-Quality Construction</strong></p>\n\n<p>A home is a long-term investment, and Shivalik Group understands the importance of quality construction. We maintain rigorous standards to ensure that every brick laid is built with durability and craftsmanship.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>These developments, particularly in Ahmedabad, reflect Shivalik Group&#39;s commitment to transforming the city&#39;s real estate landscape.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Enjoy the Best Returns &amp; Quality of Life With Shivalik Group</p>\n\n<p>Choosing Shivalik Group for your real estate investment in Ahmedabad isn&#39;t just a decision; it&#39;s a step towards a secure, financially rewarding, and sustainable future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For those who seek not just a home but an investment in their future, Shivalik Group is the answer.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Your dream home is just a step away with Shivalik Group.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n-&nbsp;Kishan Thakkar</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Homes","tag_lower":"homes"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Investment","Homes","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Investment,Homes,Ahmedabad","published_time":1697394600,"published_date":"16 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1697465638,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:43 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"16 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"07:43 PM"},"updated_at":"","updated_at_time":"","is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/why-investing-in-real-estate-is-the-best-move"},"id":204,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"why-investing-in-real-estate-is-the-best-move","image":"banner_1697289317_8.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1697289317_8.jpg","banner_title":"Why investing in real estate is the Best Move","title":"Why investing in real estate is the Best Move","description":"<p><strong>The Real Wealth Generator: Why investing in real estate is the Best Move</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nOne of the safest and most profitable financial decisions one can make is investing in real estate. Real estate presents investors with a concrete and possibly profitable opportunity, as opposed to the erratic nature of stocks or the uncertainty of other investment possibilities.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tangible Asset with Intrinsic Value</strong></p>\n\n<p>Real estate&#39;s tangibility is one of the main reasons it stands out as a top investment option. You purchase a material object with inherent worth when you invest in real estate. Buildings and land have intrinsic value that frequently increases over time. Many other investments cannot compare to the sense of security that this concrete nature offers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Consistent Income Stream</strong></p>\n\n<p>Real estate investing, especially in rental homes, can offer a steady and dependable revenue source. Rental income delivers a consistent revenue flow that may be utilised to pay costs, reinvest, or save for future goals, unlike other investments where you must rely on market volatility.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Diversification of Investment Portfolio</strong></p>\n\n<p>Real estate is a fantastic means of achieving diversification, which is a fundamental component of successful investing. When other investments in your portfolio are more volatile, adding real estate assets can help distribute risk and offer stability.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tax Benefits</strong></p>\n\n<p>Real estate investing has several tax benefits. Taxes on real estate, mortgage interest, and some maintenance costs may all be deducted. Real estate investment is also frequently encouraged by the government through tax advantages, making it an even more alluring choice.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Legacy and Generational Wealth</strong></p>\n\n<p>You may leave your family a lasting legacy by investing in real estate. Future generations can get properties from you, giving them a priceless asset that can safeguard their financial future.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Control and Customization</strong></p>\n\n<p>Real estate gives you direct control over your investment, in contrast to several other investments over which you have only limited authority. To raise the value and rental revenue of your home, you might manage, renovate, or update it.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nThe bottom line is that real estate investing is a tried-and-true method for accumulating money, establishing financial security, and ensuring a happy future. Real estate offers a route to financial success that can&#39;t be overlooked, whether you&#39;re an experienced investor or just getting started. To gain from the many advantages real estate has to offer, think about making a wise choice and including it in your investment portfolio.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-Bhavya Shah</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"}],"tags_array":["Real Estate","Investment"],"tags_commaseparted":"Real Estate,Investment","published_time":1697221800,"published_date":"14 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1697289317,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:45 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"14 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"06:45 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 16, 2023","updated_at_time":1697438522,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/the-role-of-technology-in-real-estate-investment"},"id":203,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"the-role-of-technology-in-real-estate-investment","image":"banner_1697204755_3.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1697204755_3.jpg","banner_title":"The Role of Technology in Real Estate Investment","title":"The Role of Technology in Real Estate Investment","description":"<p>The combination of technology and real estate investing is not just a fad; it is a powerful force that is changing the landscape of the sector. The importance of technology in real estate investment cannot be emphasised as we traverse the digital world. Technology is altering the possibilities and potential returns in real estate investment, from utilising blockchain and virtual reality (VR) to exploiting big data and artificial intelligence (AI).</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Making decisions based on data</strong></p>\n\n<p>The accessibility of enormous volumes of real estate data has given investors access to insights and analytics that were previously unthinkable. Investors may now make data-driven decisions by examining aspects such as property valuations, rental trends, and neighbourhood growth patterns thanks to sophisticated algorithms and machine learning models.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Property Search and Evaluation</strong></p>\n\n<p>The process of finding properties has become easier. In order to find the appropriate property, investors can save time and effort by filtering and comparing possibilities using online platforms and mobile apps, which give them access to broad property listings.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Virtual Property Tours</strong></p>\n\n<p>A revolutionary new approach to tour properties without actually going there has been made possible by virtual reality (VR) and 3D image technology. Investors can view a property&#39;s potential from the convenience of their devices.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Property Management</strong></p>\n\n<p>Apps and tools for managing rental properties make the job easier. Rent collection, maintenance requests, and tenant communication are just a few of the chores that investors can handle effectively, improving the entire management process.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Risk assessment</strong></p>\n\n<p>It is done using AI-driven algorithms, which also help to reduce the risks related to real estate investments. Investors can develop ways to safeguard their money and obtain insight into future problems.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Market Insights</strong></p>\n\n<p>It gives investors a deeper understanding of current market conditions and new business prospects. Making informed investment decisions is made possible by this information.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\nTechnology&#39;s involvement in real estate investing goes beyond simply modernising processes; it also involves giving investors the tools they need to make wiser decisions, expedite processes, and maximise returns. Technology&#39;s impact on the real estate industry will only grow as it develops.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-&nbsp;Bhavya Shah</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Technology","tag_lower":"technology"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"}],"tags_array":["Technology","Real Estate"],"tags_commaseparted":"Technology,Real Estate","published_time":1697135400,"published_date":"13 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1697204001,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:03 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"13 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"07:03 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 13, 2023","updated_at_time":1697204755,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/how-gandhinagar-and-ahmedabad-will-grow-together"},"id":200,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"how-gandhinagar-and-ahmedabad-will-grow-together","image":"banner_1697035532_42.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1697035532_42.jpg","banner_title":"Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad Will Grow Together","title":"How Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad Will Grow Together","description":"<p><strong>What is Twin City?</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>A twin city is a concept of linking two or more cities, towns, regions or states that share some common characteristics, such as culture, industry, history or geography. The purpose of twinning is to foster friendly relations, cultural exchange, economic cooperation and mutual understanding between the linked entities.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>How has the government introduced Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad to become twin cities?</strong></p>\n\n<p>The Gujarat government has recently announced that Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad will be officially declared as twin cities.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>This decision was taken to promote the integrated development of both cities, which are located about 30 km apart and have a combined population of over 8 million people.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nThe government plans to implement various projects and schemes to improve the connectivity, infrastructure, governance and quality of life of the residents of both cities.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Some of the initiatives include:</strong></p>\n\n<p>- Developing a metro rail network that will connect Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad and reduce the travel time between them.</p>\n\n<p>- Creating a unified development authority that will oversee the planning and execution of urban projects in both cities.</p>\n\n<p>- Establishing a common civic body that will provide municipal services such as water supply, drainage, sanitation, solid waste management and street lighting in both cities.</p>\n\n<p>- Setting up a joint police commissioner that will ensure law and order and security in both cities.</p>\n\n<p>- Building a world-class convention centre, sports complex, cultural centre and botanical garden in Gandhinagar to attract tourists and visitors from Ahmedabad and other places.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>How will real estate be benefited from it?</strong></p>\n\n<p>- The twin city concept is expected to have a positive impact on the real estate sector in both Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad. Some of the benefits are:</p>\n\n<p>- Increased demand for residential and commercial properties in both cities due to improved connectivity, infrastructure and amenities.</p>\n\n<p>- Enhanced value appreciation for existing and new properties in both cities due to increased economic activity, employment opportunities and social development.</p>\n\n<p>- More options for buyers and investors to choose from a variety of properties in both cities according to their preferences, budget and lifestyle.</p>\n\n<p>- More scope for developers to launch innovative and sustainable projects in both cities that cater to the needs and aspirations of the customers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<br />\n<strong>How will our projects at Adani Shantigram, Vaishnodevi &amp; Bhat get twin city benefits?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Our projects at Adani Shantigram, Vaishnodevi &amp; Bhat are strategically located near both Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nThey offer premium residential and commercial spaces that are designed with modern architecture, quality construction and luxurious amenities. They also provide easy access to various educational institutions, healthcare facilities, shopping malls, entertainment zones and recreational areas.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>By being part of the twin city concept, our projects will get twin city benefits in terms of:</strong></p>\n\n<p>- Better connectivity to both Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad via metro rail, road network and public transport.</p>\n\n<p>-Higher value appreciation due to being part of an integrated urban development plan that will boost the economy, society and environment of both cities.</p>\n\n<p>- Greater customer satisfaction due to being able to enjoy the best of both worlds - the greenery and tranquillity of Gandhinagar and the vibrancy and dynamism of Ahmedabad.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n<p>The twin city concept is a visionary idea that will transform Gandhinagar and Ahmedabad into smart, sustainable and livable cities.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>It will also create immense opportunities for the real estate sector to grow and flourish. Our projects at Adani Shantigram, Vaishnodevi &amp; Bhat are ideally positioned to leverage these opportunities and offer our customers an unmatched living experience.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We invite you to explore our projects and discover how they can make your dreams come true.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;\n<style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #cccccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}-->\n</style>\nPiyush</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Twin City","tag_lower":"twin city"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"},{"text":"Gandhinagar","tag_lower":"gandhinagar"}],"tags_array":["Twin City","Ahmedabad","Gandhinagar"],"tags_commaseparted":"Twin City,Ahmedabad,Gandhinagar","published_time":1696962600,"published_date":"11 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1697035532,"date_format":"","date_time":"08:15 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"11 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"08:15 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 11, 2023","updated_at_time":1697035710,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/the-remarkable-rise-of-shivalik-skyview:-85-sold-in-just-2-weeks!"},"id":199,"project_id":"174","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"the-remarkable-rise-of-shivalik-skyview:-85-sold-in-just-2-weeks!","image":"banner_1696942353_24.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696942353_24.jpeg","banner_title":"The Remarkable Rise of Shivalik Skyview: 85% Sold in just 2 Weeks","title":"The Remarkable Rise of Shivalik Skyview: 85% Sold in just 2 Weeks!","description":"<p>The world of Real Estate is filled with stories of success, failure, rises, and falls.<br />\nSome narratives captivate our minds and evoke astonishment to know more about a particular real estate magnate. In the bustling world of real estate, it&#39;s not every day that you come across a story as eye-catching as Shivalik Skyview&#39;s. Just think about it: selling 85% of their units in a mere two weeks is no small feat. It&#39;s almost like a new movie being entirely sold out on its opening weekend! That&#39;s a sign that there&#39;s something truly special about Shivalik Skyview.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWhat makes this even more fascinating is the burning question on everyone&#39;s mind: How did they manage to get such overwhelming interest and sales quickly? Well, that&#39;s the story we&#39;re about to dive into. Let&rsquo;s unpack the journey of Shivalik Skyview and discover the magic behind those two incredible weeks.&nbsp;Whether we are looking to buy a property, sell one, or just be interested in real estate stories, understanding what made Shivalik Skyview, so popular can teach us a lot.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><br />\nFactors leading to the early sales of Shivalik Skyview&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>1. Strategic Location<br />\nLocation remains a paramount factor in the real estate industry. Shivalik Skyview is not just built in a city but is strategically located in a rapidly growing part of the city- &ldquo;The Gift City- Gujarat International Finance Tec-City.&rdquo; With excellent connectivity and tucked among developing commercial complexes and IT hubs, Shivalik Skyview seemed ideal for individuals prioritising ease and luxury.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n2. State-of-the-art Amenities<br />\nWith ranging from top-notch amenities, Shivalik Skyview wasn&rsquo;t just offering a place to live but selling a lifestyle. From world-class fitness centers, a rooftop swimming pool offering delightful skyline views and kids&rsquo; areas to smart home features. They promise a luxurious and convenient future.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n3. Pricing<br />\nWhile luxury was a cornerstone of Shivalik Skyview&#39;s strategy, it managed to strike a balance, ensuring accessibility without compromising on grandeur. Setting the pricing just right struck a balance between exclusivity and accessibility. This made the project appealing to the high earners and the mid-income segment.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n4. Reputation and Trust<br />\nThe developers behind Shivalik Skyview had a firm root of delivering quality projects on time. For buyers, investing in a property isn&rsquo;t just about the here and now; it&#39;s about ensuring timely completion, adherence to promises, and post-sale service.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n5. Future Growth Prospects<br />\nThe area surrounding Shivalik Skyview is not just developing but is projected to be a significant hub in the next five years. Investors quickly spotted this, realizing that purchasing an apartment here is not just for living but also promised substantial ROI in the upcoming years.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nConclusion<br />\nThe success of Shivalik Skyview was about reading the market&#39;s pulse, understanding buyers&rsquo; needs, and delivering beyond expectations. It has become a phenomenon and a testament that the results can be legendary when product quality meets resourceful marketing and genuine customer value. The Success Story of Shivalik Skyview will be recounted in the history of real estate for years to come.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-Nidhi&nbsp;Raikundaliya</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Shivalik Skyview","tag_lower":"shivalik skyview"},{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"}],"tags_array":["Shivalik Skyview","GIFT City"],"tags_commaseparted":"Shivalik Skyview,GIFT City","published_time":1696876200,"published_date":"10 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696942353,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:22 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"10 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"06:22 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 10, 2023","updated_at_time":1696944093,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/your-home-in-india’s-next-financial-hub:-gift-city"},"id":197,"project_id":"174","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"your-home-in-india’s-next-financial-hub:-gift-city","image":"banner_1696855094_81.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696855094_81.jpeg","banner_title":"Your Home in India’s Next Financial Hub: GIFT City","title":"Your Home in India’s Next Financial Hub: GIFT City","description":"<p>Have you ever dreamt of living in a place where urban living seamlessly intertwines with cutting-edge technology, creating a utopian environment with a vibrantly flourishing city life? Homeownership is an aspiration for every individual. While buying a home in conventional city areas may be mainstream, imagine residing in a futuristic city amid world-class infrastructure, where innovation meets sustainability, and businesses thrive alongside nature.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWelcome to GIFT City &ndash; Gujarat International Finance Tec-City, a visionary project that has garnered significant attention and investment in recent years. This article explores compelling reasons to consider buying a home in GIFT City and why it should be on the radar of potential and upcoming homebuyers.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nGIFT City boasts state-of-the-art infrastructure, representing a harmonious blend of business and luxurious living spaces. It offers world-class amenities, including modern road networks, a robust public transport system, landscaped gardens, exclusive recreational areas, fitness centres, and uninterrupted, seamless services. When you choose a home here, you become part of a thriving international community. Moreover, the city&#39;s strategic location ensures easy access to Ahmedabad and Gandhinagar, allowing you to enjoy the amenities and opportunities of both these cities.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nIn a world transitioning towards sustainable and climate-resilient practices, this futuristic city is committed to sustainability and green living. It is designed with a thoughtful approach to minimizing its carbon footprint, adopting energy-efficient practices that encourage environmentally friendly living. Therefore, buying a home in GIFT City also means investing in a sustainable, greener and healthier future.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nEnvisioned as the next financial powerhouse of the country, GIFT City is host to major financial institutions, global banks, insurance companies, and stock exchanges. This creates a robust economic environment, generating immense job and business opportunities, with the city serving as the nodal hub for business activities. Additionally, the city&#39;s proximity to the &#39;Knowledge Corridor,&#39; home to some of the top educational institutes, opens doors to enhanced career opportunities right in your neighbourhood.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nInvesting in a home in GIFT City is not just a lifestyle choice but also a smart investment decision. As economic activity flourishes, property values are expected to appreciate. The rapidly growing ecosystem has witnessed increased demand, exemplified by Shivalik&#39;s recent project, Shivalik Skyview, which saw nearly 85% of homes booked in just two weeks. Buying a home here offers not only a comfortable and convenient lifestyle but also the potential for substantial returns on your investment in the long run.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nOwning a home in GIFT City is not merely securing a living space; it&#39;s investing in a location poised for economic success, offering comfortable and luxurious living at the heart of India&#39;s future financial hub. It&#39;s not just a home; it&#39;s a place where dreams are built, futures are secured, and sustainability is prioritized. The Shivalik Group&#39;s ambitious project encompasses all these amenities, combining the best of both worlds.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nConsider buying a home in GIFT City and become a part of India&#39;s ambitious journey towards becoming a global financial hub!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-Sharvari Parikh</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"GIFT City","tag_lower":"gift city"},{"text":"Home in GIFT City","tag_lower":"home in gift city"}],"tags_array":["GIFT City","Home in GIFT City"],"tags_commaseparted":"GIFT City,Home in GIFT City","published_time":1696789800,"published_date":"09 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696854746,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:02 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"09 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"06:02 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 09, 2023","updated_at_time":1696855094,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/right-time-to-invest-in-ahmedabad-is-now!"},"id":196,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"right-time-to-invest-in-ahmedabad-is-now!","image":"banner_1696687197_27.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696687197_27.jpg","banner_title":"Right time to invest in Ahmedabad is NOW!","title":"Right time to invest in Ahmedabad is  NOW!","description":"<p>The Gujarat government has taken several steps to boost the real estate sector in the state. There are many factors contributing to this success story where the purchase affordability of property remains on top as the capital value for the land remains significantly lower than the other fast-developing states.</p>\n\n<p>According to some studies, the real estate sector is likely to touch a cap of $1 trillion by 2030. The sector is likely to produce 100 million jobs by the end of the decade with the share of skilled workforce expected to rise from 9.7% in 2023 to 10.5% by 2030. This growth is expected to arise from all domains of the construction sector like- real estate, infrastructure development, affordable housing, commercial assets, etc. The commercial market sector has surged a substantial 33.3% from the previous quarter. Gujarat has emerged as a dark horse in the race of the hot real estate market where metro cities like Bangalore, Mumbai, Delhi, etc. are some other key players.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nWidely recognised market researchers&#39; study states that Ahmedabad was the most affordable housing market in India in 2022 with an affordability ratio of 22%. (Affordability ratio is calculated by dividing house prices by gross annual workplace-based earnings.) The city enjoys excellent connectivity to the rest of the state and the addition of new town-planning schemes being developed hand-in-hand with the population demand are boosting a vibrant residential and commercial real estate in the city.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nAhmedabad, being the Twin-city of Gandhinagar is also set to see growth momentum with the development of GIFT city. Some 55 lakh square feet of residential real estate space is coming up on the campus with an investment of 2700 crores over the next five years. With the provision of premium infrastructure, the average prices of housing are on the higher end. The positivity in the market is driven by the fact that people are upgrading their lifestyles, so residential real estate will gain good momentum.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Investing in real estate in Ahmedabad and Gandhinagar (as Twin-cities) is a lucrative opportunity given the range of residential properties that can provide attractive ROI. The Shivalik group has been able to capitalize on this opportunity to bring the best quality of&nbsp;residential real estate in the city with futuristic design of buildings i.e &ldquo;Shivalik Skyview&rdquo; has its design inspired by a drone, &ldquo;The Curv&rdquo; will have one of its kind curved design in India with ultra-modern amenities to suit the next generation buyers and investors. So the right to invest in Ahmedabad is NOW!</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Investment","tag_lower":"investment"},{"text":"Ahmedabad","tag_lower":"ahmedabad"}],"tags_array":["Investment","Ahmedabad"],"tags_commaseparted":"Investment,Ahmedabad","published_time":1696617000,"published_date":"07 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696687198,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:29 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"07 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"07:29 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 07, 2023","updated_at_time":1696687329,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/anticipated-trends-in-the-2023-residential-real-estate-landscape"},"id":195,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"anticipated-trends-in-the-2023-residential-real-estate-landscape","image":"banner_1696600472_45.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696600472_45.jpg","banner_title":"Residential Real Estate Trends in 2023","title":"Anticipated Trends in the 2023 Residential Real Estate Landscape","description":"<p>The realm of Indian residential real estate is in constant flux, adapting to the shifting preferences of homebuyers. In this dynamic environment, industry experts are shedding light on the housing categories poised to capture prospective buyers&#39; attention this year.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Sustainable Residences for a Green Future</strong></p>\n\n<p>Millennials, now active participants in the housing market, are attuned to the virtues of sustainable living. This has sparked a surge in the demand for eco-friendly homes. The younger generation meticulously assesses properties based on their Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG) credentials. Many are willing to invest a five to seven percent premium if it means acquiring a home with superior sustainable amenities and benefits that promise long-term value. Developers quickly recognise this shift and proactively incorporate green elements into their projects. Expect to see properties that boast abundant open spaces adorned with lush greenery, bathed in natural light, and featuring enhanced air and water quality.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Versatile and Opulent Living Spaces</strong></p>\n\n<p>With freelancing, side hustles, and remote work arrangements now commonplace, every family member seeks sanctuary within the home. The evolving work culture has transformed the homebuyer&#39;s mindset, placing a premium on spacious, sustainable, and ultra-modern residences equipped with cutting-edge green technology. Today&#39;s ideal home provides convenient access to recreational opportunities, transportation options, and a robust social infrastructure that caters to the needs of children and senior citizens, complete with nearby schools and healthcare facilities.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Furthermore, luxurious living is set to make a significant impact this year. There&#39;s a growing demand for homes with mesmerising sea views and expansive outdoor spaces, including balconies, terraces, courtyards, and nearby gardens and parks. Contemporary consumer preferences have shifted from premium real estate to a more sophisticated approach. Buyers desire a lifestyle that seamlessly accommodates remote work while preserving the luxury and comforts of luxurious living.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Driving Forces Behind the Market</strong></p>\n\n<p>Millennials have emerged as a driving force in the real estate sector. Post-pandemic, we&#39;ve witnessed a surge in homebuying among married couples and single millennials, regardless of their marital status or gender. They have been instrumental in propelling the momentum of the real estate market, resulting in record-breaking sales. The pandemic&#39;s uncertainties have amplified the need for homeownership and real estate investment, making millennials the linchpin of the industry&#39;s resurgence.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>As the sands of time continue to shift, the Indian residential real estate landscape is evolving to meet the desires and needs of its discerning clientele. Sustainable living, versatile spaces, and luxury amenities are the facets that are expected to shine brightly in 2023, drawing in homebuyers seeking homes that offer both sanctuary and style.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>-&nbsp;Jayshree Ochwani</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Trends","tag_lower":"trends"},{"text":"Real Estate","tag_lower":"real estate"},{"text":"Residential","tag_lower":"residential"},{"text":"2023","tag_lower":"2023"}],"tags_array":["Trends","Real Estate","Residential","2023"],"tags_commaseparted":"Trends,Real Estate,Residential,2023","published_time":1696530600,"published_date":"06 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696600472,"date_format":"","date_time":"07:24 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"06 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"07:24 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 06, 2023","updated_at_time":1696600521,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/celebrating-women-at-shivalik"},"id":192,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"celebrating-women-at-shivalik","image":"banner_1696511459_13.jpeg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696511459_13.jpeg","banner_title":"Celebrating Women at Shivalik","title":"Celebrating Women at Shivalik","description":"<p>History was scripted on the night of 21st September 2023 when The Constitution (One Hundred and Twenty-Eighth Amendment) Bill, 2023, seeking to reserve 33% of seats in Lok Sabha and state Assemblies for women, was passed unanimously by Rajya Sabha. Women&#39;s reservation in politics empowers women at various levels. It not only encourages more women to participate in politics but also inspires women to take on leadership roles in other sectors.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nHaving an all-inclusive work culture in its true sense, the Shivalik group has always been a supporter of women&rsquo;s empowerment. Although Real Estate is perceived as a male-driven industry, the Shivalik group has been changing this mediocre mindset by motivating and promoting women employees to build their careers in the Real Estate industry by offering them key positions in decision-making.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nShivalik group believes the following listed skills that women possess, prove their mettle in any walk of life:</p>\n\n<p>1. Learning attitude:<br />\nScience has shown that girls typically mature more quickly than boys. They not only have a knack for learning, but they also pick things up more quickly.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n2. Prioritizing Integrity:<br />\nWomen never hesitate to take hard steps if those steps do any good to their families. Women with their higher integrity do great in the business world.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n3. Ability to Build Relationships:<br />\nWomen have the ability to build relationships faster, which boosts the chance of their being successful.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n4. Flair for Lean Methodology:<br />\nWhen it comes to lean techniques, women excel. No women consider making a sizable purchase immediately soon, whether using their own funds or those of investors.</p>\n\n<p><br />\n5. Soft Corner for Human Management:<br />\nWomen excel in managing human resources and have a greater grasp of the emotional side of business. This aids in the effective management of both people and the company. Additionally, because of their higher emotional intelligence and intuitive nature, they can successfully arbitrate any conflict in business.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nIt is notable that the Shivalik Institute of Real Estate, established to bridge the skill gap in the Real Estate industry, is led by Mrs. Dipali Shah (W/o Mr. Chitrak Shah, Founder &amp; Chairman, SIRE) as Founder and director, SIRE. &nbsp;In the Parent company, &lsquo;Shivalik&rsquo;, the key position of Sales dept. head are also held by Women Employees.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nThe group celebrates womanhood by providing a home-like &amp; healthy work environment for women employees to impart a sense of belongingness. Many events and meet-ups are arranged for women employees exclusively to have quality time They are also provided with perks such as Maternity leaves. Women&#39;s power is the backbone at Shivalik and we celebrate it.</p>\n","seo_title":"","seo_description":"","seo_keywords":"","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags_array":"","tags_commaseparted":"","published_time":1696444200,"published_date":"05 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696511459,"date_format":"","date_time":"06:40 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"05 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"06:40 PM"},"updated_at":"","updated_at_time":"","is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"},{"share_url":{"website_url":"https://www.shivalikgroup.com/articles/pioneering-sustainable-living-for-a-greener-tomorrow"},"id":189,"project_id":"","page_id":"","joint_page_id":"","slug":"pioneering-sustainable-living-for-a-greener-tomorrow","image":"banner_1696412029_27.jpg","image_full":"https://www.reecosys.com/api/image-tool/index.php?src=https://www.reecosys.com/assets/uploads/blog/banner/banner_1696412029_27.jpg","banner_title":"Pioneering Sustainable Living for a Greener Tomorrow","title":"Pioneering Sustainable Living for a Greener Tomorrow","description":"<p>In an age where climate change is a global concern, it&#39;s imperative to rethink the way we build and live in our homes. The real estate industry, often a significant contributor to environmental issues, is undergoing a transformation towards sustainability. Leading this change is Shivalik, a name synonymous with innovation and trust in the real estate sector.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>The Environmental Challenge</strong><br />\nThe environment faces unprecedented challenges due to urbanization and the construction industry&#39;s activities. Traditional construction methods, heavy resource consumption, and high energy usage have put a massive strain on our planet. As awareness of these issues grows, there is a growing demand for eco-friendly, sustainable housing solutions.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Shivalik&#39;s Commitment to Sustainability</strong><br />\nShivalik, with its legacy spanning over two decades, is no stranger to innovation. The company has embraced the challenge of building homes that not only meet the highest standards of luxury and comfort but also minimize their environmental impact. Shivalik recognizes that sustainability is the need of the hour and is committed to a greener, more sustainable future.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Energy-Efficient Design</strong><br />\nShivalik&#39;s journey towards sustainability begins with energy-efficient design. Their projects incorporate advanced architectural principles that maximize natural lighting and ventilation. This not only reduces the need for artificial lighting and heating but also ensures a healthier living environment for residents.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Renewable Energy Integration</strong><br />\nTo further reduce the carbon footprint of their projects, Shivalik integrates renewable energy sources. Solar panels, for instance, are a common sight in Shivalik communities. These panels harness the power of the sun to generate electricity, reducing the reliance on non-renewable energy sources and lowering electricity bills for homeowners.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Water Conservation</strong><br />\nWater, a precious resource, is conserved diligently in Shivalik&#39;s projects. Rainwater harvesting systems are incorporated into the design, allowing rainwater to be collected and used for landscaping and flushing, reducing the demand for municipal water supplies.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Green Spaces and Biodiversity</strong><br />\nShivalik understands the importance of green spaces for both the environment and residents&#39; well-being. Their projects feature meticulously planned green areas, providing a haven for local flora and fauna. These green spaces not only enhance the aesthetics but also contribute to the overall ecological balance.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>In conclusion, Shivalik stands at the forefront of the sustainable housing revolution. Their dedication to building eco-friendly, energy-efficient, and environmentally responsible homes is not only a testament to their commitment to quality but also to a greener tomorrow. By choosing Shivalik, homeowners aren&#39;t just investing in luxurious living; they&#39;re investing in a better future for themselves and the planet.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>- Aakash Shah</p>\n","seo_title":"Pioneering Sustainable Living For A Greener Tomorrow","seo_description":"Pioneering Sustainable Living For A Greener Tomorrow","seo_keywords":"Pioneering Sustainable Living For A Greener Tomorrow","seo_image":"","seo_image_full":"","tags":[{"text":"Sustainable","tag_lower":"sustainable"},{"text":"Sustainability","tag_lower":"sustainability"},{"text":"Green Homes","tag_lower":"green homes"}],"tags_array":["Sustainable","Sustainability","Green Homes"],"tags_commaseparted":"Sustainable,Sustainability,Green Homes","published_time":1696357800,"published_date":"04 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":1696412030,"date_format":"","date_time":"03:03 PM","created_at_show":{"created_at":"04 Oct, 2023","created_at_time":"03:03 PM"},"updated_at":"Oct 05, 2023","updated_at_time":1696490238,"is_active":1,"master_user_id":"1","master_user_id_add":"","is_notify_to_user":"1","is_deleted_request":"0","is_approved":"1","approved_date":"","email_subject":"","email_body":"","added_by":"shivalik group","added_by_type":"admin"}]
